Body: Make sure you've made a SWAP!  Dear VINchain community,  For those of you who have not yet made their token swap, the deadline is fast approaching! The MEW (My Ether Wallet) website is being updated and they are removing the ability to swap tokens. There is no specific date set when the website will fully transition to the new version. When this happens, everyone who has not yet swapped their tokens will no longer be able to do so. That is why it's SUPER important for everyone who was not yet made their token swap to do so as soon as possible!  What is a token swap? We distributed tokens to everyone who participated in our ICO. These tokens have to be ‘activated’ (or ‘swapped’) before they can be used, traded, sold, etc.  How do I know if I have to swap? 1) You have to do the token swap if you: 2) Participated in the VINchain ICO 3) You got tokens airdropped to you 4) You have VINchain tokens in your wallet  How do I swap my tokens? 1) Go to https://www.myetherwallet.com/ 2) Scroll down to the column "MEW" and click on the "Vintage" button 3) Now follow these instructions:    - Video Tutorial: https://youtu.be/mwQOIzOiRHQ or    - Written Instructions: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-swap-your-tokens-af58bc2237ba 4) After the token swap is done - activate your wallet: https://medium.com/@vinchain/instructions-to-activate-the-vinwallet-5167d0c5106b  Thank you for your continuous support!  Stay up to date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all the news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: An inside look into the development of the VINchain connected car platform  The VINchain connected car platform 🚗  The VINchain connected car platform consists of a device that can be plugged into your vehicle (also known as an “OBD device”) as well as the sophisticated VINchain infrastructure that interprets the data from your vehicle. The VINchain connected car platform allows you to connect with your vehicle like never before… and get rewarded for it!  Some of the top features of the VINchain connected car platform include: - Getting rewarded for sharing your data - Have full control of what you share and what you keep private - Being able to track your vehicle’s location via GPS - Monitoring the condition and diagnostics of your car - Integrate your car with your other smart devices - Getting custom notifications about vehicle events that are important to you - Create geo-fences and get notified when your vehicle enters or leaves that area - Easily track every move of your car or the car of your loved ones - Get notified of any possible accidents - Get notified if your car gets towed - Get roadside assistance if you need help - Have a record of all of your trips for easy business reporting / trip logging - Get suggestions for how you can save money by driving more efficiently ....And much more!  Take a closer look and read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/an-inside-look-into-the-development-of-the-vinchain-connected-car-platform/305

Body: VINstuff #34 (March 1 - March 31)  Dear VINchain community,  First and foremost we would like to thank every VINchain supporter! We have a great community which inspires us to work hard and make all of our plans come to fruition. As you may know, the majority of our solutions / products have been developed, but as the saying goes “software is never finished” - and so we continue to make further developments and today we would like to share with you our latest news.  Check out our video with today's announcement: https://youtu.be/ttc6jAFpgDQ  1) VINchain Blockchain as a Service (BaaS)  Blockchain has many benefits for businesses in all sectors, but implementing a blockchain solution can be very difficult and intimidating. This is why we are so excited to announce that we have released the VINchain Blockchain as a Service (BaaS). We have made a turnkey solution for businesses to get the most out of blockchain, without having to worry about difficult integrations and frustrating nuances. Businesses of all types can now utilize the VINchain blockchain and implement their own custom currency - custom tokens, and customize the functionality of the blockchain for their specific business needs. More information and detailed use cases in our next update!  2) The VINchain connected car platform  The connected car platform, created and developed by VINchain, consists of a device that can be plugged into your vehicle (also known as an “OBD device”) as well as the sophisticated VINchain infrastructure that interprets the data from your vehicle. The VINchain connected car platform allows you to connect with your vehicle like never before… and get rewarded for it!  Take a closer inside look and read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/an-inside-look-into-the-development-of-the-vinchain-connected-car-platform/305  3) VINchain making waves across the UK  We’re one step further in our expansion and quest to bring VINchain to Europe by way of the United Kingdom. We have some thrilling updates to share about our growth in Edinburgh, London and beyond. We’ve devoted ourselves to examining the ecosystem and opportunities of the region and have met with valuable investors to secure mentorship and funding.  Read more: https://vinchain.io/blog/vinchain-making-waves-across-the-uk/301  4) Content highlight  Make sure you didn’t miss these highlights from our recent blog content.  How blockchain is making car ownership easier https://vinchain.io/blog/how-blockchain-is-making-car-ownership-easier/296  Blockchain automotive revenue opportunities https://vinchain.io/blog/blockchain-automotive-revenue-opportunities/297  Thank you as always for your great support. If you’re looking to get more involved, be sure to join our Telegram channel below, where you can chat directly with our team and founders!  Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements. Body: VINchain vehicle history reports will be available for purchase next week!  Dear VINchain community,  We are happy to announce that starting from the next week we are going to provide the opportunity for you to purchase our VINchain vehicle history reports with both tokens or fiat. Moreover, 90% of the amount that will be received in fiat will be converted into VIN tokens, which will be purchased from an exchange.  Our vehicle history reports are sourced from over 350+ million VIN records that are stored in our blockchain. We welcome you to check out the breadth and depth of our reports by following this link: https://vinchain.io/report/check  You can look up the history of any car simply from its VIN number. Enter the VIN into the search box and click “check VIN”. You will then see a small preview report that contains the preliminary data. If you would like to see more information, choose the appropriate method of payment (fiat or VINchain token) - click on “get report”.  We are not solely focused on the US market, our project has wide reaching global applications. Next week we are starting to scale our operations in Europe. Stay tuned for the exciting news to come!  Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements. Body: VINstuff #35 (April 1 - April 30)   Dear VINchain community,  As always we are excited to bring you good news. In today's VINstuff we’ll cover what we’ve been up to in the month of April. Thank you to our great community for your support - together we will revolutionize the automotive industry!  Check out our video with today's announcement: https://youtu.be/Vpz0Ncep6qs  1) Reports sold so far  Over the course of the last year or so we have been providing access to some of our data for free. We did this to build up interest in the project, showcasing the vast amount of data that we collected and to show the automotive industry that we are serious about vehicle history. Only a week ago we began selling our VINchain vehicle history reports and we are very happy to see great traction. In just this one week we sold 575 full reports. Thank you all for such amazing support and let’s continue to move full speed ahead!  As we have stated in a previous announcement, 90% of the amount that we receive in fiat will be converted into VIN tokens, which will be purchased from exchanges. We honor our promises and this week we bought out 823,524 tokens. The buy back wallet address is: https://wallet.vinchain.io/account/vinchainbuyback1  You can check our reports here: https://vinchain.io/report/check  - VIN tokens and Fiat accepted  2) VINchain launched in Europe!  We are so excited to venture into new territories and explore new possibilities. The first country that we venture into is Sweden. The US is still our main focus, but the time has come to branch out and continue our quest to bring transparency to the automotive industry worldwide. The Swedish version of the website can be found here: https://vinchain.io/sv/   Read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/vinchain-launched-in-europe/308  3) Technical update  Alongside launching in a new country, we have also made some updates to our website ( https://vinchain.io/) to reflect all of the developments with the Vehicle history reports, Connected car platform, BaaS (Blockchain as a  Service) and custom tokens.  The development is ongoing, we are doing our best to make our visions come to fruition. Now you can learn more detailed information about the vehicle while enjoying the beautiful new layout of the report.  Our ultimate goal is to help fight vehicle fraud - utilizing our mileage verification check and our blockchain technology we help do just that! Our blockchain guarantees that the information in our reports has not been altered. With the development of our sophisticated tools, we can reduce odometer manipulations by detecting and reporting them! That’s why it's very important to always get a vehicle history report before purchasing any used vehicle.  Read more: https://vinchain.io/blog/upgraded-vinchain-vehicle-history-report/312

Body: VINchain prepares for NADA Show 2019  Dear VINchain community,  Time has flown by and the most important automotive event of the year fast approaches. NADA Show 2019 takes place in San Francisco from January 24-27 and VINchain is overjoyed to confirm that we’ll be in attendance.  The NADA Show Expo is the largest marketplace of products and technologies, industry leaders, manufacturers, exhibitors and other key players, and presents a tremendous opportunity for growth. We are planning to pitch our vision and idea and court partnerships in order to expand our already extensive vehicle data network. Our primary focus at this year’s show is to connect with large dealerships through our connected car solution, the VINchain Connected Car Device. We’ve received overwhelmingly positive feedback from dealers and are excited to offer a product that will allow them to expand their traditional approach with 21st century tools.  This is one show you won't want to miss if you’re in the industry or area and we look forward to meeting our community and preaching the benefits of VINchain.  Our CEO Alex Miles will be attending the show at booth 7808W (https://www.nadaconvention.org/NADA2019/Public/eventmap.aspx?MapID=78&MapItBoothID=140075&MapItBooth=7808W) between 10:30am and 6:00pm (follow the link on the number of the booth and refer to the detailed map to find us). Be sure to come say hello if you’re in attendance!   All NADA activities will take place in the Moscone Center. The show will have programming in all three buildings, Moscone South, Moscone North and Moscone West. You can check NADA show website (https://www.nada.org/) in case of any changes to the location.  Check the schedule of the event here: https://show.nada.org/2019/Schedule/.  We are thrilled to have the opportunity to present at the largest and most prestigious event across the entire automotive industry.  Hope to see you there! Body: NADA Show 2019 wrap-up  Dear VINchain community,  After completing a successful run at NADA Show 2019 we’re glad to be back at our offices with more on our docket than ever. We’re grateful to have met many members of our community and want to extend a thank you for coming to our booth to say hello.  The expo was a resounding success for VINchain, we received positive feedback the VINchain Connected Car Device, our onboard diagnostic (OBD) solution. We’ve forged a tremendous amount of connections that will soon blossom into partnerships, specifically with large dealerships.  We knew dealerships were interested in our connected solution, but we’re astounded by the amount of excitement we were able to generate. The features with the most amount of hype were the ability of our device to install in one easy step, plug and play with no pairing needed are a busy dealer’s dream. They enjoy the streamlined user-interface for both their employees and customers through our app, ensuring that all users have a painless experience. Further, they appreciate our dealer-specific offerings, including our dedicated dealer portal and fleet management. Our fleet tracking solution has no cap in size and allows businesses to keep their ear to the ground on one of their most valuable investments, their vehicles.  With the simplicity of install, dealers are able to pass on the benefits to their customers by selling our device. This not only levels-up the relationship with customers’ vehicles, it empowers them to earn VIN tokens with their data, an opportunity unique to VINchain.  In short, our insider knowledge of the automotive industry and continued willingness to integrate feedback into our solution is paying off in spades. Stay tuned for exciting developments as partnership agreements are finalized, and thank you for your ongoing support. Body: VINchain Making Waves Across the UK  Dear VINchain community,  We’re one step further in our expansion and quest to bring VINchain to Europe by way of the United Kingdom. We have some thrilling updates to share about our growth in Edinburgh, London and beyond. We’ve devoted ourselves to examining the ecosystem and opportunities of the region and have met with valuable investors to secure mentorship and funding.  We had the pleasure of visiting the University of Edinburgh Incubation Programs, where we spoke about blockchain technology, our approach to data collection and about what it means to innovate.  Next, we were able to get acquainted with Codebase, who help spread ideas among like-minded startups, learning specificities across the industry.  We enjoyed a session at Galvanise Capital which outlined how to structure and conduct business in Scotland, and also met with lawyers and venture capital investors.   Met at Scottish Enterprise Session with ecosystem players and visited SkyScanner - a leading global travel search site which allows businesses to learn how to increase positive communications with clients.  We were able to secure a productive session at Google, paving the way for some incredible future growth - we’ll be able to share more details at a later date!  Another session was held with FieldFisher, a European law firm with market-leading practices across many of the world's most dynamic sectors.  We were able to secure a workshop with Mike Butcher, an 'Editor at Large' of TechCrunch, the largest breaking-news site covering the world’s hottest tech companies.  Visited EBRD to learn how the huge corporation do their business.   One of the most surprising events was with Pitch@Palace. The Duke of York founded Pitch@Palace in 2014 to provide a platform to amplify and accelerate the work of entrepreneurs and provide opportunities to interface with people who can help make their business dreams a reality at St. James’s Palace. This brought unique chance to make a small pitch to the prestigious guests of the event and evangelize VINchain’s vision.  Techstars is well known across the startup world as a premier worldwide network helping entrepreneurs succeed. We had the great pleasure of attending their Startup Bootcamp, which provides guidance on how to be accepted into the best accelerators and competitions. We wrapped up the day with an excursion to the Facebook office.  Pitching at UK Belarus Startup Roadshow / Pitch Night was a great opportunity to wide a range of contacts one more time and make sure there is some niche for the VINchain in UK. We’ve been pushing our idea to different communities, gaining some useful contacts and plenty of experience.  We’re elated that our passion to evolve the automotive industry and now we are focused on our development in Europe and Great Britain. We make sure that the UK market can offer us some great opportunities and in terms of our recent experience are now continuing the development in all directions.  Thank you for your continued support!

Body: VINstuff #29 (November 26 - December 9)  Dear VINchain community,  We’ve got some exciting developments on the horizon to share with our one-of-a-kind community. VINchain has been developing at a breakneck pace and we’re continuing to focus on our growth through partnerships and extension of our data marketplace. To this end, we are excited to be attending the National Automotive Dealerships Association (NADA) Show next month, by which time our connected car platform will be up and running. Until then, we’re well on our mission to keep putting out more content for the industry.  Check out our video with today's announcements: https://youtu.be/ktmayZROiJA  1) NADA Show 2019  VINchain will have a booth while we attend NADA between January 24th through 27th, be sure to come say hello if you’re in attendance. The event is perhaps the largest across the entire automotive industry and an ideal place to spread our vision while expanding our partnerships. This is especially important at this stage of our growth as we’re focused on growing our data marketplace by joining up with large vehicle data providers. We look forward to the enormous opportunity and hope to see you there!  2) OBD platform  We’ve reached a point in our growth where we’ve decided that our behind-the-scenes development is suitable to focus on the VINchain Connected Car Device. This is known as an onboard diagnostic (OBD) device and makes any car as smart as your phone. The device itself relies on a platform to be useful to everyone from consumers to large enterprise and fleet owners, we’re committed to making our OBD platform usable in beta by the time we attend NADA at the end of January.  Read more about the VINchain Connected Car Device at: https://vinchain.io/connected-car  3) Targeted content videos  As the year wraps up, we’ll be producing targeted content in the form of short videos for our website. As VINchain provides benefit to so many distinct audiences, we want the message and opportunity we provide to be clear to whoever it is visits our website, from dealerships and manufacturers to enthusiasts and laypeople. Keep an eye out for these videos and other updates to our website.  4) Content highlight  If you’re interested in learning more about the automotive industry and crypto space, be sure to check out our recent blog content you might have missed.  The Difference Between Security Tokens And Utility Tokens: https://vinchain.io/blog/the-difference-between-security-tokens-and-utility-tokens/276  9 Ways To Increase Fleet Efficiency: https://vinchain.io/blog/9-ways-to-increase-fleet-efficiency/274  Thank you as always for your continued support. Body: VINstuff #30 (December 10 - December 23)  Dear VINchain community,  We have an exciting update regarding the direction VINchain will continue to grow in the future and some stellar content to share. If you’re hungry for information on the path for VINchain and the future of the automotive industry, this is the update for you! After all, we’re grateful to count blockchain and automotive enthusiasts (dorks) among both our team and supporters.  Check out our video with today's announcements: https://youtu.be/5A9H8eaE1Ok  1) VINchain Connected Car partners  As we develop our onboard diagnostic (OBD) device and platform (branded as VINchain Connected Car Device), we are committed to partnering with dealerships and service centers. We believe our device platform is vital to develop as the means to produce first revenue and demonstrate the incredible utility of our blockchain data marketplace. With the National Automotive Dealership Association (NADA) Show fast approaching, we are devoted to courting mutually beneficial partnerships. We believe having a beta OBD platform is the most surefire way to accomplish this while highlighting the strengths of VINchain.  If you represent a dealership or service center, reach out to info@vinchain.io to learn more.  2) VINchain Big Data  Our plans to launch data analytic services (branded as VINchain Big Data) are something that many of our followers may not be aware of. Across all industries, all modern, hugely successful companies share one similarity: their ability to utilize data to guide their decisions.  An old saying reminds us that to be forewarned is to be forearmed, that knowledge is power. This power can be used to better serve customers by better knowing their needs, to more efficiently engage resources like fleet vehicles, to guide marketing and sales decisions and more-- the sky's the limit. Data sets are only limited by the quality and scope of the information used, which is why VINchain remains devoted to building the largest and highest quality vehicle data marketplace.  Our data analytic services empower companies with blockchain information to most effectively guide their business through the treacherous terrain of the automotive sector and beyond.  3) 2019 Roadmap  The holidays are traditionally a slower time of year for business, as people spent time with their loved ones and travel. With this in mind, we’re focused on the future of VINchain in 2019 and will be updating our roadmap as the new year rolls around-- stay tuned for exciting developments still to come.  We’re grateful as always for our incredible community, be sure to join the conversation on Telegram to talk directly with the team!  4) Content highlight  We’ve continued to produce specialized content for our blog in order to inform and educate our community and beyond. Be sure to check out our two most recent articles on what makes VINchain stand out from the crowd and some tips for dealers to keep customers around. Body: VINchain 2018 Wrapup  As the year comes to an end it’s the perfect time to remember and reflect on what we have succeeded in and are proud of.  2018 was an incredible year for VINchain, we’ve started to bring our vision to life and continue to work hard on our development. There will be more updates to come but for now let’s highlight achievements of our passionate team and community.  This year was full of events that enabled us to spread our idea across the industry, form valuable connections and even win competitions.  We attended the Digital Dealer Conference & Expo in Orlando, eMerge Americas expo, Emerge conference in Minsk, IoT World where we entered and won the “Project Kairos” startup pitching competition. We participated in the Annual Summit World Tokenomic Forum, took part in the “Connected & Autonomous Vehicles 2018” conference, Global Entrepreneurship Week in Belarus, competed in the Belbiz Startup Battle on the GEW stage which was held with the support of the British Embassy and more. We’re poised to hit the ground running in 2019 with new conferences and events that we’ll share with our amazing community.  We had an extremely fruitful year developing our MVP, hosted webinars with our CEO, onboarded a large team of experienced in automotive industry advisors, became members of automotive associations including ASA (Automotive Service Association), NIADA (National Independent Automobile Dealers Association), MOBI (Mobility Open Blockchain Initiative) and GAVDA (Global Alliance for Vehicle Data Access). We forged promising partnerships with A Better Bid, Autoinspect, Epic VIN, VinGurus, CarsDesk, Easy Export, Vininspect, AdvertiseCarsFree, DASH, ZEUS Protocol, UnbiasedAuto and continue to grow. We released an updated version of our website which is now live and listed VIN tokens (VIN) on two top exchanges - IDCM and IDAX.  We’ve continued to produce specialized content for our blog in order to inform and educate our community and beyond. Be sure to check out what we do in our official announcement channel: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements and ask directly any questions in our group: https://t.me/vinchainio.  We wish you a happy New Year and hope you meet your goals as easily as VINchain!  Regards, The VINchain team

Body: The Growing Importance of the Internet of Things (IoT) in Our Daily Lives  The internet of things (IoT) is defined as “the interconnection via the Internet of computing devices embedded in everyday objects, enabling them to send and receive data.” In plain English? IoT is the ability of various devices, objects, vehicles, homes, and other ‘things’ to communicate with and interact through the internet. Simple.  This opens up a world of possibility for both the ‘thing’ involved and the user, from being able to change the temperature in your house and keeping track of your vehicle’s location through your phone to turning on your favorite song and lighting setup with an audio command. All these benefits have one thing in common, they empower you to have greater control over your life and the things in it with greater convenience.  Let’s explore some more of the potential and benefits of internet of things together below.  Read more: https://vinchain.io/blog/the-growing-importance-of-the-internet-of-things-iot-in-our-daily-lives/283

Body: Problems with Vehicle History Reports  Vehicle history reports are extremely useful, if not critical when buying a vehicle. These reports provide information on things like previous damage, maintenance, odometer rollbacks, and how many owners a vehicle has had. However, not all reports are created equal. Most of the popular vehicle history providers promise the world, but rarely deliver. By solving the problems most people encounter with current providers, VINchain is shaking up the industry with their revolutionary vehicle history reporting system.  Read more: https://vinchain.io/blog/problems-with-vehicle-history-reports/285

Check out our video with today's announcement: https://youtu.be/AISewC_8DX0  1) SONIC Automotive  We recently enjoyed a tremendous chance to pitch the VINchain solution to one of the largest automotive dealerships in the country, SONIC Automotive. We were fortunate to be able to present both our vehicle data marketplace and connected car solution. They were especially receptive to our connected device and the included fleet tracking, presenting an incredible opportunity not only in itself through SONIC, but in receiving feedback to inform our approach to upcoming events.  2) Fleet tracking and NADA  The fast-approaching NADA Show is the most enormous and prestigious automotive events of the year, and we remain laser-focused on poising ourselves for success. Our main focus at this year’s show is to partner with large dealerships through our connected car solution, the VINchain Connected Car Device. In order to make our offering as valuable as possible, we are tailoring the device to have as much utility and value as possible by offering unparalleled fleet tracking, thanks to the input we received from SONIC Automotive.  3) Content highlight  Make sure you didn’t miss these highlights from our recent blog content.  The Growing Importance of the Internet of Things (IoT) in Our Daily Lives: https://vinchain.io/blog/the-growing-importance-of-the-internet-of-things-iot-in-our-daily-lives/283  Problems with Vehicle History Reports: https://vinchain.io/blog/problems-with-vehicle-history-reports/285  Thank you as always for your great support. Body: How GPS car tracking devices work  Global Positioning System, or GPS, is a way to accurately determine the location of something on earth, and is considered one of the most important technologies of our time. It uses a combination of satellites and receivers to pinpoint the geolocation of these receivers along longitude and latitude coördinates. Information is supplied by around 30 purpose-built satellites orbiting the earth in fixed orbits. This information can then be interpreted by software the can display the position in a more user-friendly way by using map overlays.  GPS has a myriad applications, including military, civilian transport navigating, personal navigation, map making, climate studies, emergency location, as well as commercial applications such as fleet monitoring and courier tracking.  Read more: https://vinchain.io/blog/how-gps-car-tracking-devices-work/249

Let us know which of our products or related technologies you want to learn more about and we’ll be sure to create content that fits your needs.  As always, we appreciate the support of our incredible community. Look out for VINstuff every other week.  3) How GPS car tracking devices work   Global Positioning System, or GPS, is a way to accurately determine the location of something on earth, and is considered one of the most important technologies of our time. It uses a combination of satellites and receivers to pinpoint the geolocation of these receivers along longitude and latitude coördinates. Information is supplied by around 30 purpose-built satellites orbiting the earth in fixed orbits. This information can then be interpreted by software the can display the position in a more user-friendly way by using map overlays.  GPS has a myriad applications, including military, civilian transport navigating, personal navigation, map making, climate studies, emergency location, as well as commercial applications such as fleet monitoring and courier tracking. We’re constantly updating the website and we’re enthused to offer a fully updated, more convenient service for checking the validity of information. You can view the updates to the verifier at: https://validate.vinchain.io/.  The new system is designed to verify all of the information that's contained inside the reports from our partners. In order to get all necessary information verified, simply enter the code received earlier from our partners.  Read more about the updated VINchain Data Verifier at:  https://vinchain.io/blog/major-upgrade-to-the-vinchain-data-verifier/261   2) VINchain will take part in Global Entrepreneurship Week in Belarus  We are happy to announce that we’ve been selected for Global Entrepreneurship Week in Minsk (https://tinyurl.com/ydgoz73a), an annual, global event that connects people, businesses and enterprise from over 170 countries. We’ll take part in a key event, the First National Tradeshow of Innovative Companies and Startups (Startup-circle), also held in Minsk from November 12th - 14th, 2018. This unique event will gather business representatives, investors, international experts and more in one place, making it a great opportunity for VINchain to gain new connections and spread word of our vision.  Our Belarusian team will be in attendance and we would love to meet all of you who will pass by. We are ready to tell you everything about VINchain. While attending the First National Tradeshow of Innovative Companies and Startups, we are planning to find new opportunities for our project, build new partnerships, and spread the idea of VINchain to the world.  You can read more about our attendance at this event at:  https://vinchain.io/blog/vinchain-will-take-part-in-global-entrepreneurship-week-in-belarus/259  3) Updated IDCM Listing Date  Unfortunately, the IDCM exchange is undergoing maintenance this week and has delayed the date of listing VINchain to the 12th of November. Though some of our community may be frustrated by the change, progress on the exchange will proceed as normal and the delay was simply due to an unexpected update to their platform. We still look forward to a beneficial relationship with IDCM.  A quick highlight on the exchange for those of you not in the loop: IDCM covers more than 60 countries and regions across the world and holds the title of the first exchange alliance built upon a node consensus mechanism. It will work together with IDCG’s own DApp platform (based on DPoS) and DAICO incubation platform to create a complete blockchain ecosystem. You can find out more about IDCM on their website at: (https://www.idcm.io/).     4) Why tracking your car is important  What if car owners could use their smartphones to interface with their car? They could enjoy GPS tracking of their vehicle, request roadside assistance, keep an eye on their kids and carefully monitor the condition of their car. All of these are made possible by VINchain.  Read more: https://vinchain.io/blog/why-tracking-your-car-is-important/262  5) How blockchain technology helps to increase the value of your car  VINchain uses blockchain technology to provide accurate, comprehensive, and up-to-date vehicle history information. This information can help increase the value of your car.  Read more at: https://vinchain.io/blog/how-blockchain-technology-helps-to-increase-the-value-of-your-car/258  Thank you for your enthusiastic support, none of our progress would be possible without our incredible community. Body: Special announcement - The VINchain block explorer is live on our website!  Dear VINchain community,  We’re delighted to announce that we’ve launched VINchain Block Explorer and it is currently accessible on our website. We’re constantly working to develop our system and it’s the highlight of our week when we have progress like this to share.   Ok so all of this sounds exciting, but what is a block explorer?  Generally when you have a blockchain, you need something to be able to scan every block and see whats inside. This is what makes blockchains transparent. A blockchain scanner does exactly that - it helps users easily see what's inside individual blocks and helps keep track of all of the transactions that happen in the network. For those who have used the website etherscan.io this is very similar to that. With the aid of our blockchain explorer you will be able to view all transaction histories and balances of addresses. Right now you can navigate to our website (vinchain.io), click on PRODUCTS in the top bar, and select VINchain Block Explorer from the dropdown menu.  All transaction histories can be seen for all those who are interested. Be sure to check it out if you’re even half the blockchain enthusiast (geek) we are! As always, thank you for your continued support, all of our progress is made possible by our supportive community. Body: VINstuff #21 (September 10 - September 16)  Dear VINchain community,  It’s our favorite time of the week again already, when we get to share our progress with our stellar community. We’ve been focused on the development of our website and the system itself and have exciting updates in the works. Thanks to the support of our community our journey is sure to be successful.  Check out our video with today's announcements: https://youtu.be/yJmUx7BVKIE  1) VINchain Block Explorer is now available for use!  We’re delighted to announce that we’ve launched VINchain Block Explorer and it is currently accessible on our website. We’re constantly working to develop our system and it’s the highlight of our week when we have progress like this to share.   Sounds exciting, but what is a block explorer? Generally when you have a blockchain, you need something to be able to scan every block and see whats inside. This is what makes the technology transparent. A blockchain scanner does exactly that - it helps users easily see what's inside individual blocks and helps keep track of all of the transactions that happen in the network. For those who have used the website etherscan.io before, this is a similar technology. With the aid of our blockchain explorer you will be able to view all transaction histories and balances of addresses. Right now you can navigate to our website (vinchain.io), click on PRODUCTS in the top bar, and select VINchain Block Explorer from the dropdown menu.   All transaction histories can be seen for all those who are interested. Be sure to check it out if you’re even half the blockchain enthusiast (geek) we are!   2) Website update  As our system has a wide range of appeal across consumers and sectors of the automotive industry, we want our website to reflect that. We’ve been developing specialized sections so every user visiting our website has a satisfying and informative experience, whether they’re a consumer looking at our OBD device, or a dealership looking to partner with us. Updates will go live next week, so keep your eyes open!  What would you like to know more about VINchain and what content do you love to see? Do you wish we had more videos explaining the intricacies of our system, or want to hear more about our partner’s developments? let us know on our Telegram or social media below! Body: VINstuff #22 (September 17 - September 23)  Dear VINchain community,  We’re grateful for the opportunity to share another week of progress with our supportive community. We have several projects in the pipeline and development on our current projects is moving forward at a meteoric pace. Our audience is hungry for the future and we are ensuring each of the products we offer is in their best possible form as we move forward.  Check out our video with today's announcements: https://youtu.be/wrxiOav_1uI  1) Fleet Tracking Platform Development  Our biggest and most tangible achievement of this week is that our fleet tracking platform (gps.VINchain.io) is almost available for use and it’s well worth the wait.   The platform is designed to service the largest fleets on the road, small-scale operations looking to grow and everything in between. Our fleet management solution will track vehicle and driver statistics, maintenance records, fuel stats and more, providing unprecedented communication with your assets and drivers. It will allow your routes, drivers and vehicles to be as efficient as possible, saving you money in wear & tear and more.  Soon it will be available for testing firsthand.   2) Content Evolution Continues  One of the most difficult challenges we face is also one of our greatest strengths, that we offer diverse benefits both to consumers and multiple sectors of the automotive industry. While this is one of our most compelling selling points, it also makes it difficult to cater our content to all of these audiences simultaneously and consistently. We are currently in the process of rewriting and producing more content specifically targeted at each of our audiences. Soon, our website, social media and content will fully reflect the multifaceted nature of our business and provide a streamlined and informative experience for everyone from dealers to consumers.  What would you like to know more about VINchain and what content do you love to see? Do you wish we had more videos explaining the intricacies of our system, or want to hear more about our partner’s developments? Please let us know on our Telegram or social media below.  3) Looking for New Exchanges  The most common question we receive from our community is in regards to getting listed on more exchanges. We have begun to focus more on this aspect as our development continues, though our main priority continues to be on delivering the highest quality product possible. It’s important to understand that this very focus is what separates us from many blockchain startups that will come and go in the blink of an eye.  Listing on exchanges is only as useful for us as far as we can offer a truly developed and complete product which then gives value to our company and contributors. To be blunt, our goal has never been to make a quick buck and run, we are fully committed to revolutionizing the automotive industry.  As always, thank you for your continued support. Body: VINstuff #23 (September 24 - September 30)  Dear VINchain community,  We’re excited to share another week of progress with you all. We’ve been focused on bringing our content up to speed to match our development and perfecting our offerings behind the scenes. While we love sharing headline-worthy updates with you, the subtleties of our business are just as vital to our success. This week we’ll be highlighting a few features some of our audience may not be aware of.  News: Website Update  We’re beginning to roll out our website updates this week to provide a more streamlined, specialized experience. We’re launching a section devoted to those looking to become a VINchain partner which caters directly to our many audiences. Further, the main drop down will feature sections linking to instructions to get a demo, get the device, and to learn more about our connected vehicle solution. We’ve heard your feedback and we’re adding a section on the main page to make it easier to find interviews with our expert advisors. Even more website updates in the coming weeks!  Highlight: VINchain Connected Vehicle Device  Our app teams up with our connected vehicle device to make your car smarter after a simple plug-and-play install. This simple solution enables a host of benefits outside of the ability to earn VIN tokens and we want to overview some of them for you.  Diagnostics Your car, smarter. A check engine light just isn’t enough information, why is every device connected now besides the most expensive investment we make? Diagnostics give peace of mind on your safety and insight into any problems so you can know what to expect before walking into the mechanic.  Driving analysis Get scored on aggressive driving, excessive idling and efficiency in order to fine-tune your driving, reduce wear & tear and save money on gas.  GPS tracking The geolocation system allows you to track your trips, set custom points of interest (POI) and personalize geofences around your work, home and more. This feature lets you put a close eye on a new teenage driver or keep tabs on a whole fleet of vehicles.  Gamification You’ll be able to compare scores against your friends and family to finally settle the bet on who’s the better driver. Find out if your husband or wife has earned the right to backseat drive.  Crash data One of the least well-known features of our device is also one of the most unique. When the accelerometer detects a sudden stop event, it records crash data with accurate timestamps. This information can be vital protecting you in a lawsuit or insurance claim.   We are always looking for feedback from our incredible community. We want to hear what you want to hear. Do you love short, informative videos on our features, a tour of our office or in-depth interviews with our advisors? We’re here to make the content you want.  Check out our video with today's announcements: https://youtu.be/mYQwn9Ip6OE  As always, thank you for your continued support. Stay tuned for a headline-worthy update in the works. Body: VINchain Partners With Zeus Protocol  Dear VINchain community,  We’re elated to announce that we have teamed up with Zeus Protocol. While all of our partners are incredibly valuable in their own right, most are focused around increasing the size of our data network. Joining forces with Zeus Protocol provides the unique ability to enhance our network by supplying context for our vehicle data through utilization of their analytics platform.  Zeus Protocol is a 2nd layer network for Ethereum (ETH), which focuses on providing the network with key innovations to support applications with scalable computation, interoperability, identity and off-chain information. Their first solution, ZeusID (http://id.zeusprotocol.com/), will provide partners and clients with decrypted on-chain identity and insightful reputation analytics, which will enable significant advantage over competition. ZeusID is one a core capability of theirs as it further strengthens one of the biggest pain points of the blockchain ecosystem — trust & reputation. They’re proud to claim over 30 million ETH wallets with a reputation score, miner verification, wallet persona and graph — all algorithmically verified.  Zeus Protocol and VINchain are incredibly synergistic as we stand firm together for the secure and reliable application of blockchain. Together we will pave the way for a future of the blockchain and automotive industry that is trustworthy and beneficial to all.  Read more about Zeus Protocol at: https://zeusprotocol.com/  As always, thank you for your continued support. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #19 (August 27 - September 2)   Dear VINchain community,   We’re excited to continue our growth into the fall and hope autumn finds you all well. Even though it seems like our Initial Coin Offering (ICO) was just last week, we have months of growth under our belts since. We’re excited to announce another week of development with the end of summer and more opportunities on the horizon and we’re as grateful as ever to have the support of a wonderful community.   Check out our video with today's announcements: https://youtu.be/2Ptmq-XEBLE   1) Meet Our New Partner - UnbiasedAuto!   We’re glad to announce a new partnership with UnbiasedAuto personal car buying service (https://www.unbiasedauto.com). They’ve earned a strong reputation for their services by making car buying cheaper and easier than ever and much like VINchain, their success began with a passionate team working together to deliver their common vision. We’re happy to count their specialists among our ranks and look forward to a beneficial partnership.   More about this partnership you can read here: https://vinchain.io/blog/meet-our-new-partner-unbiasedauto/236   2) Onboard Diagnostic (OBD) Device    We’ve been receiving incredible feedback on the potential of our onboard diagnostic (OBD) device from partners and industry peers and wanted to take this opportunity to highlight some of its features you might not be aware of.    The OBD device is easy to install and will have incredible value for individual consumers, families, dealerships and other companies who manage large fleets. In addition to having GPS and tracking capabilities, through the use of an accelerometer it’s capable of detecting crashes, excessive idling, aggressive driving, towing events or even theft.   The potential applications of the VINchain OBD device are almost endless. The crash data is accurately timestamped can be accessed for insurance purposes and lawsuits. Individuals and companies who maintain a fleet can assess which drivers are putting undue wear and tear on vehicles through aggressive driving and excessive idling. We’re overjoyed that the potential application of our device in coordination with our data network grows every week in stride with our partnerships.   3) Content Development Continues   The VINchain system is multifaceted and offers value to a diversity of clients, from dealerships and insurance companies to consumers and big data firms. We are focused on providing content that offers a specialized experience for each of these markets through our website and beyond. We are committed to offering more content across all the methods of interacting with VINchain, whether it is through our Twitter, Facebook or this very newsletter. Let us know about what information and content you’d love to see more of through any of our social media channels below!   Thank you for continued support. We couldn’t have made it this far without you, please comment below as your feedback is always appreciated. Body: Big Day for VINchain - We’ve Joined GAVDA!  We’re excited to announce that we’ve joined the Global Alliance for Vehicle Data Access (GAVDA) - https://gavda.org. Consisting of a large group of global stakeholders, GAVDA is united by the common goal of maintaining motor vehicle owners’ control over personal and vehicle-generated data. User control of data is central to our platform and we’re happy to be able to contribute and unify with other thought leaders around our shared vision.  GAVDA aims to achieve their goal by preserving and enhancing the current vehicle data environment which is open, secure, technology-neutral and provides direct access to real-time data by vehicle owners. Their approach engages a data access model that provides for vehicle owner control, ensures full and fair competition, protects personal privacy and advances data security. Anyone familiar with VINchain’s blockchain will recognize this is a match made in heaven for our decentralized and secure network which collects voluntary data from customers.   Our new membership brings us closer to non-governmental organizations like trade associations, public interest groups, academics, government agencies and others who share our vision and goals. We’re excited to join GAVDA’s ranks and look forward to increased productivity and new opportunities on the horizon.  Read more about GAVDA at: https://gavda.org                                         Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements. Body: VINchain Partners with TrustedCars FLEX  Dear VINchain community,  We’re delighted to announce another thrilling partnership with TrustedCars Flex (https://www.trustedcars.com/), continuing our mission to join forces with likeminded companies disrupting the automotive industry. TrustedCars Flex introduces a new paradigm of car usage by offering an all-inclusive weekly payment to access available inventory at participating car dealerships. Sign up on the app, pick your car, drive it for as long as you want or swap it for another at any time—all while avoiding the need for long-term contracts and fixed costs. They utilize Ethereum blockchain to power their token, ensuring payments are secure and verifiable.  TrustedCars Flex was named one of the most innovative blockchain projects by the Federal Ministry for Economic Affairs and Energy and is the first startup to win the coveted Gebrauchtwagen Award for their innovative used car concept and exceptional customer experience.  VINchain and TrustedCars Flex are a perfect pairing as we’re deeply committed to bringing transparency, innovation and fairness to the automotive industry. Body: VINstuff #18 (August 20 - August 26)   Dear VINchain community,   With every week that passes we have more exciting developments to share with our incredible community. VINchain is continuing our evolution across all facets of our offerings. We have been attracting new people to our already expansive team of advisors while presenting VINchain’s benefits to dealerships, manufacturers and other potential partners. We’re glad to say that every day our reach grows while making vision becomes more of a reality.   Check out our video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C3r1uwNVP3U&feature=youtu.be   1) Interview with Donald Harris   We’re elated to present our latest interview with our trusted advisor, Donald Harris. Donald is currently the Vice President of Financial Planning and Analysis at Sonic Automotive, a Fortune 500 automotive retailer. He outlines his perspective on the VINchain project and details his picture of what the future might hold for the automotive industry as a whole. He speaks to previous career experiences and how these insights apply to VINchain. We’re glad to have Don as a team member and are excited to educate our wonderful community on our partnership.     A video version of Donald’s interview is available at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XAMl2pw29Rc   2) Manufacturer Fleet Tracking Solution   Development for our OEM fleet tracking solution continues behind the scenes. Fleet management has always presented a difficult challenge to dealerships and vehicle rental platforms, so we expect to see high rates of adoption once we’ve created a product that properly delivers our vision of the solution. Stay tuned for more updates in the coming weeks!   3) Website Development   As we expand partnerships and set our sights on new markets, the demands of our web presence grow in stride. We are currently finalizing the expansion of our website, including a new dealership-focused section and more. VINchain offers benefits across dramatically diverse markets and we want to ensure that our website reflects this. Soon, every visitor to our site will leave informed and passionate about what VINchain has to offer—whether they’re a dealership, consumer or manufacturer.   Thank you for continued support. We couldn’t have made it this far without you, please comment below as your feedback is always appreciated. Body: VINstuff #15 (July 30 - August 5)  Dear VINchain community,  Another week has gone by and it's been 15 weeks today since we have finished our ICO. We can not be happier to share this amazing journey with us! As you all know we are constantly working on the development of the system and hope that you are ready for the project to show its full potential! We are extremely joyful to have such a wonderful and strong community, that are interested in our project and the bright future that stands ahead of us. Thank you so much for being with us from the start and let's reach the moon together! As always please leave your comments down below as we really value the feedback from our community!  Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rL3O5_JvEcU   1) Get 100,000 VIN tokens for free!  We have very a special announcement for you. IDAX is starting a VIN Trading Campaign, 1,000,000 VIN will be given away during this period of time! The campaign will be held on July 31st 00:00:00 - Aug 14th 23:59:59 (UTC +8).  You can find more information about the campaign here: https://vinchain.io/blog/get-100000-vin-tokens-for-free-dont-miss-vin-trading-campaign/226  2) Changes to the token swap!  Currently, after you complete the token swap you receive your tokens within 24 hours, because the token swap process has been active and available since April and a very limited amount of users still remain to go through the token swap process, we have decided to make some small changes.  Starting from August 1st after you complete the token swap you will be receiving your tokens in your VIN wallet once a week on Fridays. Every week we will be posting a list of the people who have received them to keep everyone updated regularly.  If you have any questions at all, please contact us at info@vinchain.io  or ask in our telegram chat (https://t.me/vinchainio )  3) Interview with Mark Taylor from PureCars  We are eager to share with you an interview between Alex Miles, our CEO, and Mark Taylor, our brilliant advisor. We discussed his extensive experience in the automotive industry including his career at PureCars and his 15-year journey with AutoNation, the largest automotive retailer in the US. The interview provides an expert’s insight into VINchain and we hope you enjoy listening as much as we enjoyed recording it.   As always, we look forward to your feedback and thank you for your enthusiastic support, none of this would be possible without our incredible community. Dear VINchain community,  As it was mentioned in our white paper we are creating a system where all information about a vehicle will be evaluated according to the rating of importance. That is why we would like to ask you what information you value the most. Your opinion is important to us and that's why we ask you to help us out and fill out a brief survey. This will help us understand what information you value the most when purchasing your car!  Start survey: https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/Z97B5NM  This is a 29 question form that will take about 5 minutes to complete. Please rate each question on a scale of 1 to 10 (where 1 is not important and 10 is very important)  Thank you all so much for your time, your feedback, and your participation. Your input will help shape our internal system logic, and your contribution will ultimately change the face of the automotive landscape. Let’s create an awesome system, so we can all revolutionize the automotive industry together! Body: VinInspect Fully Integrated VINchain!  Dear VINchain community,  We have Amazing news coming your way. We’re overjoyed to present to you our first live and fully integrated partnership! Starting on August 7th Consumers will have the opportunity to request VINchain approved information via our partnering website. (https://www.vininspect.com/en ). You will have the convenience of ordering a vehicle report via VINchain tokens. Each report will have the VINchain blockchain verification guarantee - so you as the consumer can rest assured that it’s worthy of your trust!  All of the information that is found on VinInspect is verified with the hashes that are on our VINchain blockchain. All users, when purchasing a report from VinInspect, can verify all of the data that is in the report. Down below is a screenshot of the verification. You click on the red ‘check’ button, and we work our magic    VinInspect will be able to accept VIN tokens as a payment method and they have access to  the whole VINchain database. The VINchain decentralized database contains hashes of records from auctions, information about crashes and accidents, vehicle photos, and all of the information that is important to you when purchasing your vehicle.  We are elated to have VinInspect as the very first fully integrated partner! The VINchain system is a unified data source for all automotive information, and key partners like VinInspect are an integral component of bringing trust and transparency to the highly fragmented automotive industry.  Join the VINchain community today and let's pave the future of the automotive industry! Body: VinInspect hosts VINchain certified reports!  Dear VINchain community,  We’re grateful to count VinInspect as one of our valuable partners and are excited to announce that they’ve successfully implemented our blockchain system.  The automotive industry is changing rapidly and is ripe to be disrupted by new technologies like VINchain. VinInspect adopting and demonstrating the power of the VINchain blockchain is an important step in our timeline of expanding in the United States and globally. As we expand our partnerships and they implement our vision, we get closer every day to revolutionizing the automotive industry as a whole.  Information stored on the VINchain blockchain is up-to-date, transparent and secure. VinInspect’s vehicle history reports will now contain information not only from their own database, but from all the data VINchain has to offer, making them more complete and reliable than ever before. Because the system is transparent and accessible by all, it offers a myriad of benefits for each participant and user. Reports contain information on auctions, crashes, repairs, owners and more!    Further, VinInspect will be able to accept VIN tokens as a payment method. They have access to our complete database and consumers will be able to see hashes in their reports that will help to track relevant information.  We’re overjoyed to see our vision become a reality and it wouldn’t be possible without our wonderful partners and community. As always, thank you for your support. Body: VINstuff #16 (August 6 - August 12)  Dear VINchain community,  Another week has gone by and we have more wonderful updates coming your way! We are extremely pleased to have a dedicated team working hard to pave the way for our projects success. This week has been huge step forward in our growth and we can’t express how delighted we are to have the support of our community to share our journey with.  1) Help us shape the future of VINchain  As mentioned in our white paper, we’re creating a system where all vehicle information can be evaluated according to a rating of its importance and quality. This rating will change the amount of VIN tokens given for supplying differing types and qualities of data. We’re asking our community what information they consider most when assessing a vehicle’s value and condition. Your opinion is vital to us and we’d appreciate a small amount of your time filling out a brief survey. Your answers will contribute directly to our research and the future of VINchain.  Participate in the brief survey here: https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/Z97B5NM  You can find more information about the survey here: https://vinchain.io/blog/help-us-shape-the-future-of-vinchain/228  2) VinInspect now hosts VINchain-certified reports  We’re grateful to count VinInspect among our valuable partners and are excited to announce that they’ve successfully implemented our blockchain into their system. VinInspect will be now able to accept VIN tokens as a payment method and offer reports certified by VINchain.  The automotive industry is changing rapidly and is ripe for disruption by novel technologies. VinInspect adopting and demonstrating the power of the VINchain blockchain is a crucial step in our timeline of expanding in the United States and globally. As we expand our partnerships, our vision comes closer to reality.  You can read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/vininspect-hosts-vinchain-certified-reports/230  Thank you for continuous support we couldn’t have made it this far without you, please comment below as your feedback is always appreciated. Body: VINstuff #17 (August 13 - August 19)  Dear VINchain community,  As another week rolls by we have more pleasant updates coming your way. We are hard at work to bring our vision into reality, constantly developing our products and finding new partners to join us on our journey. We love sharing our progress with you and appreciate your being part of our development, as none of this would be possible without you!  Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=amrPD0oPsf4&feature=youtu.be  1) Partnership with Credits Credits (www.credits.com) blockchain platform and VINchain have joined efforts to provide end users with comprehensive and credible data on used vehicles. Our vision of becoming the first decentralized and transparent automotive data marketplace will be aided by Credits synergistic aims. This agreement between Credits and VINchain allows us to be cooperative in regards to the usage of each company’s tokens. We’re excited to continue our meteoric growth across the United States and world.  More info on Credits: (Credits is a unique technological platform for the development and execution of decentralized applications based on blockchain technology and smart contracts. Credits is able to accomplish this by offerings Nodes, a client-side application that processes and stores transaction data while executing smart contract rules. They also offer a wallet and web-based version of the app which also allows users to monitor the processing of blocks, transactions, related statistics and more.)  2) IDAX trading campaign has ended We are happy to announce that the VIN trading campaign on IDAX has come to a successful conclusion. It’s been a stellar 2 weeks and we would like to congratulate all the users who participated, to see if you were one of the top traders please refer to the link below. Thank you for your continued support.  Top 3 winners: VIN Reward list: 1st. id****001@gmail.com 100000 VIN 2nd. mua.gio.bao****lut@gmail.com 80000 VIN 3rd. klaasharm****sen@gmail.com 50000 VIN  IDAX Announcement: https://idax.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360013289932-Announcement-of-the-awarding-ceremony-for-VIN-event  3) Technical development update We are continuing to evolve the technical side of our project while building out integration with data aggregators. We continue to improve and refine all of our software, such as the mobile app, blockchain, fleet tracking, website and other pursuits. Body: Dash and VINchain Partnership Announcement!                               Dash and VINchain have entered into a partnership, to leverage their joint interest in using data to improve vehicle ownership and maintenance.  Dash offers smart driving products for both consumer and business vehicles, helping make driving safer, greener and more affordable for drivers. VINchain offers a decentralized blockchain-based vehicle history report, to authenticate vehicle maintenance, repair and ownership.  The partnership will look to integrate VINchain’s technology into the core Dash products, thereby enabling users to add their real-time driving data into Vinchain's infrastructure - this will create a ledger of how the car has performed and been maintained. Users will retain ownership and control of their data in accordance with Dash's user terms (opt-in will be required) and users will receive Vinchain tokens when their individual data is used.  About Dash:  Dash is a Vehicle Intelligence Platform, offering smart driving products for both consumer and enterprise drivers. Launched in 2014, Dash has 450,000 users in over 100 countries. Product features include driver feedback, trip tracking, engine diagnostics and predictive maintenance alerts. To learn more, go to www.dash.by or email: contact@dash.by  About VINchain:  VINchain is a tamper-proof and decentralized vehicle data platform that is bringing transparency and trust to the automotive industry. With the aid of blockchain technology VINchain unites all data repositories into one common ledger and provides access to transparent data for all - enterprise and consumer. To learn more, go to www.vinchain.io or email info@vinchain.io

Body: CoinEx scam alert!  Dear VINchain community,  We are sad to say we have a warning to share with you all today. We’ve been moving forward with our focus of getting listed on more exchanges and one of them was CoinEx Market (https://www.coinexmarket.io ).  We made an agreement and prepayment (of one Bitcoin) for listing months ago, but they never integrated us onto their exchange due to their corruption and shady business practices. They started by postponing the listing process and requesting more time, now they are refusing to return the prepayment.  The invoice can be viewed here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sJXeMVyruv8mzCXhOATdZdtn3N3vIgFZLo5EdwGojn0/edit  The transaction can be viewed here: https://btc-bitcore4.trezor.io/tx/7ad69ea4a8fd8f09dde568c42322672126d44cebac98196f0868e6535945ff8b  The conversation when they agreed to refund our payment but did not do so can be viewed in our blog: https://vinchain.io/blog/223  We want to ensure our community is aware of CoinEx Market’s reputation and avoid them at all costs. These business practices and lack of transparency are exactly what we seek to solve by building the VINchain network, and we are thankful as always for your incredible support. Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #12 (July 9 - July 15)   Dear VINchain community,   We are delighted to announce the results of another week of hard work. We were able to complete our listing on the International Digital Asset Exchange (IDAX), we’re participating in the KuCoin listing competition, and we launched the alpha version of our onboard diagnostic (OBD) device!   We look forward to hearing your feedback on these developments as they wouldn't have been possible without you! Thank you for being with us from the start and let’s revolutionize the automotive industry together!   Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IftQsAHO4ic   1) VINchain is listed on IDAX (International Digital Asset Exchange)!   VINchain is listed on the IDAX exchange! (https://www.idax.mn/#/assets/deposit?coincode=VIN)  We want to apologize that it took longer than expected, but the wait is finally over. We had to overcome challenges surrounding the integration of our token as it is based on the Graphene format instead of the much more common ERC-20, but that is behind us and we are live! Please read a step-by-step instruction on how to trade VIN tokens on IDAX at: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-trade-vin-tokens-on-idax-8eed5d2eb1e4  You can read more about IDAX exchange here: https://vinchain.io/blog/216   2) VINchain is competing for free listing on KuCoin!   VINchain is enrolled to take part in the listing competition on the KuCoin exchange and we need your help! The winner of this competition will receive a free listing on KuCoin, which will be greatly beneficial to the VINchain community.  If we win the competition, all users who voted will get 5 BTC worth of VINchain tokens (in total)  To help us have the best shot in the competition, please join KuCoin’s Telegram channel (https://t.me/KuCoin_Telegram_Competition) and read the pinned message. The competition starts July 12th 18.00(UTC+8) and runs until July 15th 18.00(UTC+8).  You can read more about the competition at: https://vinchain.io/blog/217   3) The alpha version of our onboard diagnostic (OBD) device is ready!   We’re not embarrassed to say that we are technology enthusiasts (alright, maybe even nerds) and we’re overjoyed to be able to offer the alpha version of our OBD device. After our fruitful initial coin offering (ICO) period, its development has been a major goal and we’re enthused to share its progress.   We currently have 4 devices installed in vehicles and you can use our login to access them. Please login using demovin as the username and Vinchain2017 as the password to view our progress firsthand at: http://gps.vinchain.io/?lang=en   You can read more about the alpha version of our OBD device here: https://vinchain.io/blog/219   Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements.   Join the conversation on social media: Telegram - https://t.me/vinchainio Twitter - https://twitter.com/VINChain_io Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/vinchainio Blogspot - https://vinchain.blogspot.com.by Medium - https://medium.com/@VINChain Bitcointalk - https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2349186.0 Github - https://github.com/VINChain

They can find investors who buy at a price of over 200 to 400% below the ICO price. At this time in Idax you can buy with 1 ETH = 80,000 VIN. In ICO was 1 ETH at 20,000 VIN. I can not understand how you can be interested and not buy. I have already over 100k bought in the last hours at a price that was higher than now. Other projects are investing in providing incentives over time for those who trade. Recently, I have seen such a contest in Kucoin, offering for a week a total prize of 100 ETH for the first 500 as a trading volume on that currency. You can also offer an amount less than 100 ETH for the top 10 or 20 largest trading volume. I do not think it's a good option to focus on the product ignoring the importance of the exchange price. Thank you very much. Good luck!

Body: The alpha version of VINchain onboard diagnostic (OBD) device is ready!   Dear VINchain community,   We’re happy to share an exciting development with you all. After our fruitful initial coin offering (ICO) period, a major focus has been developing the onboard diagnostic (OBD) device. We’re enthused to announce that the alpha version of the OBD device is ready for use and you can check out the development!   We currently have 4 devices that are installed in cars and you can use our login to access them. Please login using demovin as the username along with Vinchain2017 as the password to view our progress firsthand at the following link: http://gps.vinchain.io/?lang=en   In the current alpha version, users can check a vehicle’s condition, speed, route, mileage and much more. After the testing phase is completed the device will be widely available so users will be able to receive it and install it in their own vehicles.    As always, thank you for your continued support—we couldn’t hit these exciting milestones without you! Body: VINchain is listed on IDAX (International Digital Asset Exchange)  We have great news that everyone has been waiting for! - VINchain is listed on the IDAX exchange! ( https://www.idax.mn/#/assets/deposit?coincode=VIN )  We want to apologize that it took much longer than expected, but the wait is finally over. We had faced some problems with the integration of our token since it is based on the Graphene format, instead of the much more common ERC-20. Now those issues are solved and we are live! The first exchange that we are traded on is IDAX ( https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/idax/ )  Here you can see a step by step instruction on how to trade VIN tokens on IDAX: (https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-trade-vin-tokens-on-idax-8eed5d2eb1e4)  Why we chose IDAX This company originated from GBC (Global Blockchain Research Center), an international blockchain research center and it’s a global digital assets service platform that is designed for blockchain exchange research.  IDAX operates from GBC high-tech industrial complex in Ulaanbaatar. The platform is designed to be trustworthy and user friendly crypto currency exchange which is supported with many functions such as multi-crypto currency, multi-language options, and multi level of security architecture that ensures a safe transaction of digital assets.  Today we are starting from this exchange! The VIN token now is available on IDAX so you can buy and sell it there! Join us today and let’s transform the auto industry! Body: https://www.idax.mn exchange will list VINchain tomorrow. This is from their official telegram:  IDAX will open VIN deposit/withdrawal and trading  Dear users ,  IDAX will launch VIN on BTC、ETH markets.  Deposit &Withdrawal Start Time: 11:00, July 10,2018 (UTC/GMT+08:00)  Trading Start Time: 18:00, July 10, 2018 (UTC/GMT+08:00)  About VIN  There are many problems in the used car industry-- One of the biggest is that used car buyers have limited information on a vehicle’s history. This can be disastrous for an important purchase if the vehicle has been in an accident or past damage has been hidden. This means that buyers are hesitant to pay full price for a used vehicle, as they must plan for any unseen issues.  VINchain solves this problem by creating a transparent and accurate vehicle history report. We’re able to accomplish this by decentralizing data and storing it on the blockchain. Vehicle data is collected from repair shops, dealers, manufacturers, and even the vehicle itself! Because the data is decentralized, it can’t be falsified, and it is accessible by all. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #11 (July 2 - July 8 )  Dear VINchain community,  We’re excited to share another week of developments with our incredible supporters. We will soon be listed on exchanges and are negotiating partnerships with major manufacturers. Thank you all for being with us through our growth, we appreciate your support of the VINchain revolution! As always, please leave comments - all feedback is appreciated.  Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=roZXkgxclF0   1) Interview with Joseph Derkos- Senior Account Executive, Digital Supply Chain Specialist at SAP. This week we were able to record a tremendous interview with Joseph, an expert in the arena of automotive sales analytics with a focus in the used and certified pre-owned market. Joseph talks about his experience in the industry while providing insight into the automotive industry and the way it is currently transforming. Further, Joseph shares his vision of VINchain and the future he sees for the company.  You can find the interview here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NR1J9tk_27c&t=316s    2) Exchange Integrations Exchanges have been a focus of ours while we have been waiting to be listed. Currently CoinEx Market has agreed to finish all integrations and list us by the 8th of July. Additionally, IDAX.mn is finishing their integrations and project having us listed by the 10th of July. We apologize for the delay, but we are sure the results will be worth the wait.  3) Partnership Development At VINchain we believe in collaboration, that it's better to work together than to compete. We are in communication with several automotive companies regarding the forging of partnerships. We cannot yet announce their identities as we are still finalizing agreements, though we are excited to share updates as things move forward. Thank you for your continued support during these radical developments.  Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Exchange Tomorrow!  We know that many of you have been patiently waiting for us to get listed on an exchange, and the date has finally arrived! As we promised, tomorrow on the 10th of July we will be traded on IDAX.mn (https://idax.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006821132-IDAX-will-open-VIN-deposit-withdrawal-and-trading )  VIN will be traded with the BTC and ETH trading pairs - the world's two most popular cryptocurrencies. Deposit and Withdrawal will start at 11:00 AM, July 10, 2018 (UTC/GMT+08:00). The trading itself will start at 18:00, July 10, 2018 (UTC/GMT+08:00).  You can convert (UTC/GMT+08) Chinese time to your timezone here: (https://www.worldtimebuddy.com/?pl=1&lid=1796236,5128581,4164138&h=1796236&date=7/10/2018%7C2 )  We know that it has taken us some time to get listed, and we sincerely apologize for that. We cannot express our gratitude to all of your enough for being with us this whole time and remaining patient while we got the entire listing situation sorted out. The whole reason for the delay is because we have a non-traditional token framework which is very difficult for all of the exchanges to list. So to get to this point IDAX had to build out a new framework on their exchange, which understandably takes a long time.  Now all of that is behind us, and we take another step towards a bright future for VINchain. Join us today and let's change the industry together! Body: Interview with Donald G. Stephenson, President of Alleghany Management Inc. and the former SVP for Volkswagen!  Prior to Volkswagen Don held director positions at Toyota in network development, retail development and after sales. As a Regional VP he managed regional operations for BMW, Lexus and Audi of America.  In this interview Donald speaks about how he understands the advantages of our business and how up to date the idea is, relying on his 30+ years of automotive experience. Donald also speaks about how important high quality and transparent information concerning the vehicle is.   We are extremely happy to have such a great person on our team!
