Body: VINchain Joins Ford, BMW, GM and Renault As Some of the Big Names to Connect with MOBI  We are extremely happy to announce that we have formed an amazing partnership with a conglomerate of giants in the auto industry, MOBI (https://www.dlt.mobi/ )  The MOBI organization is comprised of giants such as:  - Bosch  - BMW  - Ford  - General Motors  - Renault  ...and these are just to name a few.  What is MOBI? MOBI is a nonprofit organization working with forward thinking companies, governments, and NGOs to make mobility services more efficient, affordable, greener, safer, and less congested.  MOBI promotes standards and accelerate the adoption of blockchain, distributed ledger, and related technologies. They are also in the automotive industry working with vehicle identity and history. They span the entire mobility services value chain such as digital identity and history, location in space and time, supply chain, driving data markets and many others.  Why this is amazing for us? As a member of MOBI we are glad to be among such great companies with well-spread names as BMW, BOSCH, Ford, RENAULT as well as many others. The connections that MOBI facilitates are invaluable and we are a mile closer to forming partnerships with those companies as well. VINchain is thrilled about such a valuable partnership and we will continue working together towards better future! Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #10 (June 25 - July 1)  Dear VINchain community,  Another week another update! As always we have been working really hard and are ready to share the results with you. This week we have welcomed two new members to our team and a great new partnership coming our way, we couldn’t be more excited! We’ve also published the events that we will attend in the future on our website, so you can come and meet us in person. As always leave your feedback - we are always glad to hear from our community!  Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PVVrK--O-_8&feature=youtu.be&a=  1) VINchain Joins Ford, BMW, GM and Renault As Some of the Big Names to Connect with MOBI!  We are glad to announce that we have created a strong partnership with a conglomerate of giants in the auto industry, MOBI (https://www.dlt.mobi/ ). As a member of MOBI we are glad to be among these great companies such as BMW, Bosch, Ford, Renault as well as many others. The connections that MOBI facilitates are invaluable and we are a mile closer to forming even more valuable partnerships.  You can read more about MOBI here: https://vinchain.io/blog/212  2) We are elated to announce that we have two new members in the VINchain family!  Each week we are developing and moving our project further. We are glad to welcome new people who are ready to help us progress the project further with us! This week we are lucky to say that we have two new specialists with us and they are ready to add something special to the VINchain Community! Welcome to Gediminas Kalasunas - Communications Manager at VINchain.io and Nadya Yakutsenia - Community Manager at VINchain.io.  You can read more about them here: https://vinchain.io/blog/211  3) Check our website to see where we are going to be next!  We have decided to make it easier for our community to meet us. On our website you can see the whole list of events we are attending in the near future! Whether you have questions, suggestions or want to meet our core team members, we are always glad to see you! We are honored to have such a supporting community and would thank you for being with us all this time! We are looking forward to seeing you!  You can check the list of events here: https://vinchain.io in the Roadshow section  4) We are also glad to say that IDAX.mn has started transaction testing!  Due to the fact that our token is not ERC-20 we have faced some problems with integration. It takes time for exchanges to complete the integration and that is the main reason we have an extended wait time. But we are glad to say that https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/idax/ has started transaction testing, and trading will start once it’s completed. Thank you so much for your understanding and for being with us! Body: VINstuff #9 (June 18 - June 24)   Dear VINchain community,   Another week, another action-packed update! This week has been incredibly productive, and we want to thank you for being with us from the start—our progress wouldn’t have been possible without you.   We have a delay with exchanges. We are waiting on the exchanges to complete the integration. It takes time as our token is not ERC-20 token. Initially we have paid for a total of 3 exchanges, but one of them turned out to be a scam and disappeared before we got listed.  https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/idax/ - confirmed that they will finish integration by the 10th of July. https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/coinexmarket/ - is planning to finish the integration on the 25th of June.  We are just waiting for the exchanges to finish the integration on their side! We appreciate your patience.  Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G12itLEu4wc   1) The VINchain Blockchain is Live!   This week we have finished the reload of our blockchain, which was needed to facilitate the refund for US citizens. We have already refunded the majority of US contributors, however those who haven’t yet confirmed their refund address need to do so inside their VINchain.io account. Refunds will continue to be processed once each week on Friday.   If you went through the token swap previously, then you need to reactivate your wallet. A step-by-step tutorial of the process can be found at: https://medium.com/@vinchain/instructions-to-activate-the-vinwallet-5167d0c5106b.   If you haven’t completed the token swap then you can do this now following our video or step-by-step instructions: Token Swap Video Tutorial: https://youtu.be/mwQOIzOiRHQ Token Swap Written Instructions: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-swap-your-tokens-af58bc2237ba  You can read more about the reload of our blockchain here: https://vinchain.io/ru/blog/208   2) The Alpha Version of VINchain iOS App is Ready!   We are excited to announce that we’re unveiling the VINchain iOS App. It is now available for download on the Apple App store for you to experience firsthand! Simply create a new account to check the history of any vehicle—we’ll even reward you 25 free tokens for your efforts. These tokens will be usable on reports, or can be saved for other services in the future. https://itunes.apple.com/by/app/vinchain-app/id1366593531?mt=8   You can read more about our iOS App here: https://vinchain.io/ru/blog/209   Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group to stay up to date on all news and developments at: https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements. Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: The VINchain blockchain is live and we are ready to go!  Dear VINchain community,  We are glad to announce that our blockchain is officially live again now! As you all know due to the changes in US legislation we had to refund all the US ICO contributors.  In order to do that we stopped the swap and suspended our blockchain for some time to process the refund. It took us a little longer than expected as we have been waiting for people to fill out the necessary documents.  Right now we have refunded the majority of US contributors. Those who haven’t confirmed the refund address need to do so inside their VINchain.io account, and they will get the refund at the end of the week. The refunds will continue to be processed once each week on Friday.  If you went through the token swap previously, then you need to reactivate your wallet so you can freely use your tokens. Please follow these instructions to reactivate your wallet: (https://medium.com/@vinchain/instructions-to-activate-the-vinwallet-5167d0c5106b  ). This guide is intended for those who have went through the token swap process already.  If you haven’t completed the token swap then you will be able to do it in your VINchain.io account later today. Here is are guides for how to do so: Token Swap Video Tutorial: https://youtu.be/mwQOIzOiRHQ Token Swap Written Instructions: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-swap-your-tokens-af58bc2237ba  After you complete the swap you will be able to see your tokens within 24 hours in your VIN wallet! Thank you all for your patience and for the support of our project.  Also we want to address the issue of the delay with the exchanges. This is all due to the fact that we are not an ERC-20 token, and so exchanges are having difficulties integrating our token into their trading platform. We apologize for this. We are waiting for our listed exchanges to finalize the integration. We will announce our official listing as soon as the exchanges are done integrating us! In the meantime we are working on being listed on additional exchanges, which we will announce as soon as they officially accept us. Body: Meet our new adviser - Joseph Derkos!  Joseph Derkos is a Senior Account Executive, Digital Supply Chain Specialist at SAP. Joe Derkos is a recognized expert in the arena of automotive sales analytics, with a focus in the used and Certified Pre-Owned market.  Joe spent nearly ten years working closely with automotive sales departments to optimize vehicle prices with predictive and advanced analytics models. He brings a new perspective to the VINchain team regarding the automotive supply chain, where blockchain technology has obvious implications.  After over 10 years of analytical consulting experience bringing solutions to SAP's customers that help them to more effectively run their businesses by harnessing the power of data he achieved the position of a Senior Account Executive, Digital Supply Chain Specialist.  Joe was named to Auto Remarketing's inaugural "Used Car Industry's 40 Under 40", holds an MBA from the University of Michigan, and Electrical Engineering degree from Michigan State University, and makes his home in the suburbs of Detroit with his wife, and two children.  We are extremely happy to have such a valuable specialist on our team and we are looking forward to see the changes that this advisorship will bring to us! Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #8 (June 11 - June 17)   Dear VINchain community,   Time flies and our weekly update is ready once again. We have been working diligently on the reload of the blockchain, as we need it to be complete for the refund of US citizens. We apologize for the delay, due to the need to update servers there is an inherent time constraint and we are aiming for it to be completed the beginning of next week. The swap will be available as soon as the blockchain is reloaded.  Check out the video with today's announcements: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Mepis_qdA8&t=18s  1) New Adviser  We are honored to welcome the valuable asset of Joseph Derkos to our advisory board. Joseph is a Senior Account Executive and Digital Supply Chain Specialist at SAP who is a recognized expert in the arena of automotive sales analytics with a focus in the used and certified pre-owned market.   With nearly ten years working closely with sales departments he brings a new perspective to the VINchain team regarding the automotive supply chain, where blockchain technology has expansive implications. Joe was named one of Auto Remarketing inaugural "Used Car Industry's 40 Under 40" and we’re elated to have him as an adviser.   You can read more about Joseph Derkos here: https://vinchain.io/blog/206   2) New Partnership  VINchain is excited to announce that we have formed a partnership with a conglomerate of giants in the auto industry known as MOBI (https://www.dlt.mobi/). MOBI promotes standards and accelerate the adoption of blockchain, distributed ledger and related technologies. Further, they provide valuable insight in the fields of vehicle identity and history.   The MOBI organization is comprised of titans such as Bosch, BMW, Ford, General Motors and Renault. We look forward to forming tighter relations with these top-tier companies.  3) Joined MotorMindz  We are joining an organization that is comprised of the very top automotive masterminds in the entire auto industry. We will be working closely with legends such as Jess Van Dongen, Jim O’Sullivan, Bruce Coventry, John Felice, and Troy McLean, and this is only just scratching the surface. The MotorMindz are a collective of approximately 60 former CEO’s and top decision makers of top Auto Manufacturers, Dealer Groups, service stations, etc. Each is a heavy hitter and we will be working very closely with them as we take our product to market.   The best part about joining the MotorMindz? We have arranged a deal with them where they will be going out to dealerships and OEM’s and selling our products and services for us!  4) Blockchain Progress  We have been working very hard to reset our blockchain. Unfortunately this process is not an easy one… if only it were as simple as restarting a computer. During this process we encountered several unforeseen hurdles that have been out of our control and we apologize for the wait. We are doing everything we can to get it back up and running as soon as we possibly can. Meanwhile, we thank you for the patience!  We are appreciative of your feedback and understanding, thank you for being such a supportive community. As always, we wouldn’t be where we are without you. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #7 (June 4 - June 10)  Dear VINchain community!  Here is our weekly update with all of the interesting developments this week! This week has been very active for us. We have made some very anticipated announcements that everyone have been looking for and done lots of things in general. We are doing our best to keep you updated about all the work that has been done by our team! As always leave your comments because we are interested in what you think! Thank you so much for being with us and for all the support!  1) Exchanges  We have officially been listed on two different exchanges. We would like to mention that it took us some time to get listed, but this was due to the fact that our token is not a standard ERC-20 format and so the process is longer. However, we have been working hard and we have 2 confirmed exchanges that we are going to be listed on:  Exchanges we will be on (starting from 18th of June):  IDAX.mn (Ranked #26 in the world by daily trading volume) https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/idax/  CoinEx Market https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/coinexmarket/  We have been closely following recent new and developments and we have decided to withdraw from the OctaEx Exchange. There has been a lot of suspicious activity going on, and we do not want to risk our communities safety.  2) Refund for US Contributors  Recently, we decided to refund US ICO participants. All the participants who have made their contributions in ETH have received their tokens back to the address they contributed from. We are processing the remainder of the refunds today (6/8/18) so if you didn't get yours yet, you will receive it very soon.  Those whom contributed with other currencies (BTC, LTE, DASH) are going to get their refund today as well. Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: OBD Production Update  As you all know we like to keep you updated with our developments, and so we would like to share with you new updates about our OBD devices.  We are working on producing our own OBD device - that thing that plugs into your car to help you capture your driving / vehicle data. Last week our team visited Teltonika (https://teltonika.lt/ ) a huge manufacturer (top 5 in the industry) of OBD devices. This is a great company with over 20 years of experience in this industry.  We analyzed their manufacturing process, and witnessed OBD devices being produced right in front of us - going from raw materials to completed devices.  We visited the location where the raw materials for the devices are stored. All of the materials are counted, tracked, and inputted into the system, they are sent to the production floor.  Also we have attended the factory itself - where the OBD devices are assembled. We made sure that during this processes the device is of high quality.  Human intervention is used seldomly, in order to minimize human error and to reduce the possibility of malfunction. At the final stage of the process a robot checks the quality of the assembled device to make sure that it is 100% exactly as it should be. With the help of a special machine, they check the 3D model how the device was assembled. After that the special robot automatically checks, calibrates and sorts GPS modules. If module does not pass the test, it is sent for revision.  And finally EACH device is tested before being sent out. The device work is also tested in different conditions such as heat, high humidity, cold and etc. This is done to ensure that every device working at 100% capacity and with utmost quality.  We took a few examples of OBD devices which we are going to be testing. We will let everyone know about our future possible collaboration with such a great company! Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff #6 (May 28-June 3)  Dear VINchain community!  This is our weekly update on all the work that we have done during the week and let you know everything that has happened in the world of VINchain over the course of the last week. We are working hard on our project and we thank you for being with us and supporting us so much! We are looking forward for your feedback!  1) News from legal team!    Due to new SEC rules and regulations our legal team has informed us that we need to return all of the collected funds to our US participants. In order for us to do so we have to re-launch our blockchain. This process will take about two weeks to complete.  Those who have gone through the token swap will just have to activate their wallets again. This process takes less than a minute to complete. Those who have not gone through the token swap, will still have to do it and then later on will have to activate their wallets. All US citizens will receive their contributions in exact amount and currency that they have contributed with.  This process is necessary in order for us to ensure that our project has a bright and flourishing future.  2) Exchanges  After this process is complete we will be tradable on exchanges. We will do our best to make it as fast as possible.  3) Development of OBD  This week a part of our team has a meeting with potential OBD providers. This is one of the largest OBD companies and is known for the quality of their devices. We have great negotiation and we are looking forward to working with them, so soon you will get more news about that!  Thank you for all your support and for being with us!  Check out our YouTube update: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHAuXCvhWII&t=6s   Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  to stay up to date on all news and developments. Body: Important announcements!  Announcing Exchanges  Today we have big news for you! We have officially been listed on three different exchanges. We would like to mention that it took us some time to get listed, but this was due to the fact that our token is not a standard ERC-20 format and so the process is longer. However, we have been working hard and we have 3 confirmed exchanges that we are going to be listed on:  Exchanges we will be on: https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/idax/ starting from 18th of June; https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/coinexmarket/ starting from 18th of June; https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/octaex/ starting from 11th of June.  We will be listed on exchanges once the refund to US participants is complete (June 11th).   Refund to US Contributors  We want to thank you for participating in the VINchain ICO. Recently, we decided to refund US ICO participants. The refund will be available starting from tomorrow (6/5/18). All the participants who have made their contributions in ETH will receive their tokens back to the address they have been paying from.  If you have received an email from us saying that we need your KYC, please make sure to confirm it ASAP! Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Weekly VINstuff #5 (May 21 - May 27)  Hello VINchain community!  Check out what we have been up to for the past week. We are glad to say that work is progressing and we are building our project bigger and better every day! During this week we have made steps to further our business and we will continue this pace of progress in the future. Thank you for being with us and as always letting us know your opinion! We appreciate any feedback!  1) Project update  New website is live!  Since we have finished our ICO, we are now shifting our focus to business development and attracting new customers and data providers. As such we have updated our website to reflect this shift of focus. In this new version you can see updated information about our company and vision. We would tremendously appreciate any feedback you guys might have for us. Let us know how we can continue to improve our website and if there is anything that is unclear. We have come a very long way since we first published our website, and we have listened to your feedback every step of the way. Your opinion is valuable to us. Email us at info@VINchain.io and let us know what you think.   You can see our new version of website here: https://vinchain.io  2) Development updates:  We are continuing to populate our blockchain with information! We have been creating digital signatures (called "hashes") of our data partners information and uploading it to our blockchain. You can see the information being uploaded as each of the new blocks forms. We are happy to be making such tremendous progress in such a short amount of time!  You can see the newly created blocks here: https://wallet.vinchain.io/ .   3) Results of the conferences  VINchain took the 2nd Place at IoT World!  Last week we have attended two conferences: IoT World and Emerge. The IoT world conference was held in California, where we entered and won the “Project Kairos” startup pitching competition! It was a very exciting time for all of us and we are happy that we got such an amazing opportunity to present our idea in front of hundreds of audience members. We took the second place in pitch contest and we are extremely happy that our idea got such a high reward!  You can read more about this conference here: https://vinchain.io/blog/195  We took part in Emerge Conference!  Another part of our team also attended the Emerge conference that was held in Minsk during last week. This conference was really productive for the whole team. We have met many experienced people who have been sharing their feedback on the development of our project. We got some great perspective connections that can grow into partnerships soon, and even got an invitation for the next conference.  You can read more about the conference here:  https://emergeconf.io  4) New Interview  The latest interview with our valuable adviser Roger Crook - the CEO at Capital Springboard. In this interview he is talking about his background and experience in the industry, his interest in the startups and his life experience in general. You can hear about the long history of his career and all the work that he has done. He is sharing his vision regarding our idea, and how it can help the world. Roger is speaking about his role in the project and how it all will affect the future of VINchain. We are extremely happy to have such a person on our team!  You can check it out here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m4_FlAwqhhM&t=337s  Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  to stay up to date on all news and developments. Body: VINstuff #4 (May 14 - May 20)  Dear VINchain community!  Here is our weekly update on everything that we are currently doing! Read all about our latest news, developments, conferences, and future plans! Our project is growing and developing further and we are happy to share our progress with you! Please leave us your feedback as we will be extremely glad to hear from you!  1) Conferences:  VINchain took second place at the "Connected & Autonomous Vehicles 2018" pitch contest!  This was the most prominent gathering of auto execs in silicon valley & the largest IoT event in the world! We was extremely grateful for the opportunity to be a part of this unique event.  You can read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/195    Also VINchain took part in the Emerge conference! There were many interested people and new creative ideas that can be implemented in our project. We have been spreading our idea and creating new connections while there. There were many talks on VC & ICO startups and investors, entrepreneurship, accelerator opportunities, marketing and sales.  You can read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/198  2) Development progress:  The VINchain Wallet is Ready!  Our team has been working hard to make it happen, and finally we are glad to announce that our wallet is ready and you can see it here (https://wallet.vinchain.io ). In order to start using your wallet you need to activate it. The guide is here (https://medium.com/@vinchain/instructions-to-activate-the-vinwallet-5167d0c5106b ). This guide is intended for those who have went through the token swap process already.  You can read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/196  The Token Swap Is Available Again!  Our swap is open again for the people who haven’t completed it before. You can see the link to the swap here (https://vinchain.io/account/swap ). While you go through the swap you will create a VINchain public wallet key and a VINchain private wallet key. KEEP THESE KEYS SAFE!!! - Just like any other keys in the world of crypto. You will need these keys to use your wallet.  You can read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/197  Also our blockchain is ready and you can see it in GitHub (https://github.com/VinChain/VINchain-blockchain ). Its open source and publicly available for everyone to analyze and see how everything works!  3) Membership  We have joined The Automotive Service Association (https://asashop.org/ ). Since 1951, the Automotive Service Association (ASA) has been the leading organization for owners and managers of automotive service businesses that strive to deliver excellence in service and repairs to consumers. So we are extremely glad to be a part of that!  You can read more here: https://vinchain.io/blog/194   Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  to stay up to date on all news and developments. Body: VINchain News!  New Website is out now!  We have been working hard on developing our project and we have very exciting news for you! We released the new version of our website and its live now. You can check it out at (https://vinchain.io/) and give us your feedback so we can continue to improve!  2nd Place at IoT World  Over the course of the last week, our team has headed to two different conferences – IoT World and Emerge. The IoT world conference was held in California, where we entered and won the “Project Kairos” startup pitching competition! It was a very exciting time for all of us and we are happy that we got such an amazing opportunity to present our idea in front of hundreds of audience members.  Emerge Conference  Another part of our team also attended the Emerge conference (https://emergeconf.io) during last week. This conference was really productive for the whole team. We have met many experienced people who have been sharing their feedback on the development of our project. We got some great perspective connections that can grow into the partnership soon, and even got an invitation for the next conference. That was an amazing experience that we are thrilled to share with you! We are looking forward for more experiences like this! Body: VINstuff #3 (May 07 - May 13)  Dear VINchain community!  This is the third week of our regular news release, where we inform you about everything that happened in the world of VINchain over the course of the last week. We are always interested in hearing you opinion so please let us know any feedback that you guys might have   1) Conferences:  This week we have attended the World Tokenomic Forum, it is an Annual Summit that was held from May 8-10, in Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands. Their aim is to connect decentralized and centralized economic institutions to create a new economic order that works for all humanity, honors innovation and secures sovereignty — this is VINchain’s purpose as well, therefore, we are glad that we have been part of this.  You can read more about it here: https://vinchain.io/blog/189   2) Swap News  As many of you know we have been undergoing our token swap for the last two weeks. Now that a sufficient amount of participants have swapping their coins, we are putting the token swap on hold while we integrate everyone's swapped coins into the genesis block - the very first block of our blockchain On Monday everyone who has done the swap will get their tokens unlocked in their new VIN wallet. ( we will post the link in Monday’s news release).  You can read about all the token swap results here: https://vinchain.io/blog/190  For those of you who haven’t swapped their coins yet, the token swap will be available again on Monday.  We have been listening to your feedback This time around we have streamlined the entire process and it will be much easier to do the token swap. We have decided to make the token swap FREE for everyone. This means that even if you missed the opportunity to swap your coins earlier, VINchain will cover the transaction fee that's necessary to swap your coins.  You can read more about it here: https://vinchain.io/blog/192  3) New adviser - Jon Arnett  We have new adviser on the team- Jon Arnett. Jon is responsible for launching Carfax in Canada and he is also the President, Consulting, Canadian Sales & Business Development at Contact At Once! a LivePerson Company.  You can read more about it here: https://vinchain.io/blog/191  Check out our YouTube update: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3YJ3drR2HHs&t=5s   Stay Up to Date: Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  to stay up to date on all news and developments. Body: VINchain will take part in the "Connected & Autonomous Vehicles 2018" conference.  Dear VINchain community,  We’ve got great news for you! We’re taking part in the conference WHERE AUTO MEETS INTERNET OF THINGS (IOT) – ENABLING THE ERA OF ELECTRIFIED AUTOMATED MOBILITY ON DEMAND. It will be held on May 14 - 17, 2018 in Santa Clara Convention Center.  This is the most prominent gathering of auto execs in silicon valley & the largest IoT event in the world! VINchain is extremely grateful for the opportunity to be a part of this unique event.  The automotive space is going through a transitional period which will shape the industry beyond recognition. It is in these periods of immense change where collaboration is key. As an industry, we need to band together to tackle the issues impeding growth, set standards enabling progress and create new partnerships across all industries.  During this great event many important topics will be discussed, including vehicle electrification and infrastructure, the evolution of ADAS and vehicle automation, enhanced connectivity and new mobility models. This is a incredible chance that will help us learn more about the industry and to facilitate the quick spread of VINchain. Many valuable connections will be made, so we are looking forward to the event. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: The VINchain Wallet is Ready!  We have awesome news for you! Our team has been working hard to make it happen, and finally we are glad to announce that our wallet is ready and you can see it here (https://wallet.vinchain.io ).  In order to start using your wallet you need to activate it. The guide is here (https://medium.com/@vinchain/instructions-to-activate-the-vinwallet-5167d0c5106b ). This guide is intended for those who have went through the token swap process already. If you have yet to complete the token swap, don’t worry – we will publishing a new guide with all of the instructions simply laid out for you really soon.   After you activate your wallet  your tokens will get unlocked in your VINchain wallet.  We want to remind you that our VIN wallet will be working on our own blockchain – our blockchain is built on bitshares fork of Graphene. Our VINchain wallet has 2 modes of operation: cloud wallet and local wallet. Your wallet will be opened in the cloud mode by default - this method maximizes security as no one will be able to find the key on the web. Later on you can convert to a local wallet if you would like. Body: Meet our new adviser - Jon Arnett!  Dear VINchain community,  We’re happy to announce our newest adviser, Jon Arnett.  Simply put, Jon boasts a lifetime of automotive software experience. He’s worked with many automotive manufacturers and has years of experience with dealerships and partners. His extensive resume includes Auto Data, Car Proof Canada and Carfax Canada. Body: Dear VINchain community,  We are thrilled to announce that VINchain is going to participate in the Annual Summit that will be held from May 8-10, in Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands.  At this event, we will have the opportunity to be a part of the most crucial conversations in cryptocurrency, policy and the global "token" economy. Also, we will create important deals and partnerships, as so many valuable people and companies will be a part of this event — we will get the chance to introduce them to VINchain.  This event is held by the World Tokenomic Forum, which is the leading international organization for enabling public-private cooperation, interoperability, and innovation, as we move toward a new economic order in a token and blockchain-based global economy.  Their aim is to connect decentralized and centralized economic institutions to create a new economic order that works for all humanity, honors innovation and secures sovereignty — this is VINchain’s purpose as well, therefore, we are glad to participate. We are looking forward to hearing all of the perspectives that such an event is preparing for us! Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: New Models are launched daily with new technology and latest features. The regular and personal medium of transport for the people is a car. They, like us, lead a life. The used Vehicle industry is part of the story where Vehicle finds its new life. A new price for the new owner. The owner who buys the car is largely unaware of the history of the car, and this creates a complex situation for the buyer. The buyer finds himself with lack of information about the vehicle. This information gap gives birth to a new third-party industry, where intermediary and agents have more leverage in the deal than the actual engaging parties.

Body: Swap results!  Dear VINchain community,  We have an announcement for you! As you all know, our system will be working on our own blockchain, which is why we have been asking you to complete the swap! The swap is on pause for now because we are calculating the percentage of people who have done it. Everyone who has completed it will have their tokens unlocked in their VIN wallet (you will get the link soon).  As for the first results, we can say that from 5131 people who have took part in the ICO, 3747 people have completed the swap which is 73.03% of participants. From 452,598,800 tokens, 381,457,198 have been swapped — which is 84.28% of all the amount of tokens in circulation.  We will collect all of the results until this Friday and make the finals. People who have bought more than 2.5 ETH still need to submit documents for KYC, so we are waiting for them as well. During the weekend, the tokens of those who completed the swap will be transferred to their VIN wallet and the work of the wallet will be tested. On Monday, you will receive all of the instructions about how to use your new wallet and your tokens will be unlocked there. Also, on Monday after tokens get unlocked, the swap will resume but with a transaction fee. The fee will be 1.5% from the amount of tokens you swap, but not more than 25 tokens! Body: VINchain is a member of NIADA - National Independent Automobile Dealers Association!  Together we will change the industry forever! VINchain is happy to announce that we are now proud members of the largest and one of the most prestigious associations, NIADA - the National Independent Automobile Dealers Association and it has been serving quality independent dealers since 1946!  We are extremely honored to be a part of such a community! Only the best and the most creative projects get the chance to join and we are happy to be one of them! This new partnership opens the doors to many opportunities.   Benefits of being a member: NIADA will provide us with information, training, and representation dedicated to the support and growth of the automotive industry. As a member we will network with the best dealers and most supportive vendors in the country, attend training and education opportunities, become a Certified Master Dealer™, take part in Dealer 20 Groups, and attend the annual conventions. This is a great opportunity to be among the companies that impact the automotive industry the most.  Credibility: NIADA accepts only the most serious and credible companies, which is aligned with its professional code of ethics. Body: Everyone, complete the token swap - while it's still free!  Tokens will be unlocked at the end of the week! As many of you already know, we have been waiting for the majority of the ICO participants to complete the token swap. Right now we can say that not enough people have went through the token swap, and so for those of you who have yet to go through the swap - Please do so now! We cannot wait any longer - and we will unlock the tokens at the end of the week!  If you don’t swap now, you will have to pay a commission later!!! Currently you can still swap your tokens without paying a commission. Once the tokens are unlocked at the end of this week, you will have to pay a transaction fee in order to complete the tokens swap. Please hurry and do the token swap now!  >> Watch Tokens Swap Tutorial VIDEO << https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mwQOIzOiRHQ&feature=youtu.be  Tokens Swap Written Instructions: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-swap-your-tokens-af58bc2237ba  Having trouble with the token swap? Don’t worry, help is just one message away! Reach out to us on Telegram https://t.me/vinchainio  with your questions and our friendly admins will be happy to assist you.  If you don't swap your tokens, they will be locked and un-tradable! If you do not swap your tokens as soon as possible, then your tokens will be locked and un-tradable! You will not be able to participate in trading your tokens on exchanges! - so please complete the token swap ASAP!  VINchain wallet release at the end of the week! After the tokens are swapped and unlocked they will reside in your VINchain wallet. The wallet will officially be released this week. Please remember that the security of your wallet is guaranteed by your private key, so ALWAYS make sure to keep your private key safe! - We cannot recover your private key if it is lost or stolen!   Questions and Answers:  Q) What is a token swap? A) As you all know we will be using our own blockchain (not Etherium) and our own VINchain wallet that you can use to store your VIN tokens! In order for our tokens to be stored in your wallet, they first have to be converted from the Ethereum based tokens that they are now, into VINchain blockchain compatible tokens. This is known as a token swap. Q) Why is a token swap necessary? A) You have to go through a token swap so that your tokens become tradable, transferable, and usable. Q) Who has to do the token swap? Body: Meet our new advisor - Don Harris!  Hello VINchain community,  We’re elated to share that we’ve added Don Harris as a new advisor to our already talented board. Don boasts a wealth of experience, currently serving as VP of Financial Planning and Analysis at Sonic Automotive, a Fortune 500 publicly-traded automotive dealer. Furthermore, he oversees the analytics group that develops pricing and inventory models for Sonic’s used vehicle supercenters. In the past he developed his expertise at one of the largest homebuilding companies and in the retail industry. He achieved a MBA from the University of Pittsburgh and a BS in finance from Pennsylvania State University.  There’s no doubt Don’s diverse expertise will help VINchain achieve our goals as we continue to spread globally and launch in the United States.  Stay up to date! Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  all the news will be published here, so stay updated! Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINstuff. #1. (Apr.16-Apr.22)  Dear VINchain community!   Starting from this week VINchain will release a weekly update on our developments, this way you will always be updated! As this is our first update, let us know what you think, we’re happy to hear feedback from our valuable community.   Main News:       1) Most importantly, our Initial Coin Offering (ICO) completed on the 15th of April. In the beginning of the week we announced all the results of the ICO. We have 840,108,901 tokens in total supply and 159,891,099 tokens will be burned.   You can read more about it here: https://vinchain.io/blog/180       2) We became members of the National Independent Automobile Dealers Association (NIADA). This great news brings our project to a whole new level and exposes us to new opportunities.       3) We have finished the distribution of tokens for the affiliate program and bounty, so all the participants can see the tokens in their wallets.   Technological Update:   This week we have started with our swap. As long as we use our own blockchain everyone must participate in the swap in order to have their tokens unlocked. We want to remind everyone of the importance of completing the swap as fast as possible as tokens will be unlocked when the majority have completed the swap.   If you are having difficulties completing the swap please watch and follow the step by step video instruction.   Token Swap Video Tutorial: https://youtu.be/mwQOIzOiRHQ   All the news about the swap can be seen here: https://vinchain.io/blog/181   Conferences:   This week our CEO Alex Miles attended the eMerge Americas expo, a premier technology event connecting the Americas and exposing us to a wealth of potential partnerships.   You can read more about it here: https://vinchain.io/blog/182   New Member:   We are thrilled to announce that we have a new member of our already expansive team. Don Harris is our new advisor and is currently serving as VP of Financial Planning and Analysis at Sonic Automotive, a Fortune 500 publicly-traded automotive dealer. There’s no doubt Don’s diverse expertise will help VINchain achieve our goals as we continue to spread globally and launch in the United States.   You can read more about it here: https://vinchain.io/de/blog/184   Coming Up:         1) We have been hard at work on our own blockchain and wallet. On Monday we will release the web wallet and next week we will launch the desktop wallet!         2) Next Monday is going to be a big day as the mainnet will be launched, so stay tuned!   Stay Up to Date:   Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  to stay up to date on all news and developments.   Join the conversation on social media:   Telegram - https://t.me/vinchainio Twitter - https://twitter.com/VINChain_io Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/vinchainio Blogspot - https://vinchain.blogspot.com.by Medium - https://medium.com/@VINChain   Bitcointalk - https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2349186.0 Github - https://github.com/VINChain

Body: VINchain at eMerge Americas!   Dear VINchain community,   We’re excited to announce that we are going to be a part of the massive eMerge Americas (http://emergeamericas.com/about-us/) expo at the Miami Beach Convention Center from the 23rd through the 24th of April. This is a premier technology event connecting the Americas and exposing us to a wealth of potential partnerships. We are among good company, as sponsors include the Knight Foundation, Medina Capital, Greenburg Traurig, A-Rod Corp, Miami-Dade County and the Miami Herald.  Join Our Telegram Announcements Channel! https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements   We’re looking forward to the opportunity to develop our position for the future and spread the word of VINchain. If you’re attending the expo come say hello at our booth. We are attending in unison with VentureHive, our Accelerator partners.  We’ll be there waiting for all who are interested, ready to connect with like-minded innovators and disruptors of the automotive industry. Thank you for all of your support, we wouldn’t have opportunities like this without it.      If you have any question don’t hesitate to contact us through Telegram (https://t.me/vinchainio). There you will have constant support 24 hours a day, 7 days a week—In fact, we are so serious about customer satisfaction, you can even talk to the CEO and founders firsthand. Author: gribble
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Here steps by step of instructions  1. Have 2fa enabled  2. Make a wallet name (keep on to the wallet name)  3. Now generate the public and private keys and store them somewhere safe (your gonna be using the "VIN××××××××××" public key that you just generated in a few)  4. (Before you go to "MEW" website, find your private key from the wallet that you stored your vinchain tokens in) now go to the MEW website and go all the way to the bottom where it says "sign message" and click on the link  5. (Before you touch the message box, there will be something that says "how would you like to access your wallet?"(this is when you need your private key from the wallet that is holding your vinchain tokens)  6. select the private key answer and put your private key in the box and then click unlock  7. Now put the public key "VIN×××××××××××" (its the public key that you generated) into the message and click sign  7. now you should have the signature code, you need to copy every single thing that was in the box  8. Now go back to Vinchain site and click "next" and paste the signature code into the box

Video Tutorial: https://youtu.be/mwQOIzOiRHQ   Written Instructions: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-swap-your-tokens-af58bc2237ba   INFORMATION: - There is no time limit for the token swap - You will not lose your tokens if you do not do the token swap - Please remember to enable 2FA first - You can do the token swap from any wallet!!! (not just MyEtherWallet) - Even if you have imtoken or any other wallet, you still go to this link https://www.myetherwallet.com/signmsg.html to create the signature   ERRORS: - Zero token error: if your dashboard is showing you that you have 0 tokens in your wallet  then don't worry, their dashboard will update tomorrow. Just wait and it will be fixed automatically - The source of the "invalid data" error that some are getting - its when you copy/paste between chrome tabs on MEW - it leaves in some space characters at the start of every line if you remove these FOR EVERY LINE it works  STILL HAVE TROUBLE? - Ask the community, everyone is very helpful - send them an email at info@vinchain.io ( topic: I HAVE A PROBLEM WITH SWAP) with exact description of the problem that you have faced. They will get back ASAP, all the problems will be solved so stay calm!

Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: How to Swap Your Tokens  Dear VINchain Community,  We are ready to distribute your tokens to all of you. In order for you to get your tokens everyone must first go through a token swap. This is a quick and easy procedure. Please take a few minutes to read the instructions carefully.  Step 1 - Before you can do a token swap you first have to enable 2FA (Two-Factor Authentication) for your account.  Instructions to enable 2FA can be found here: https://medium.com/@vinchain/vinchain-logging-in-after-the-security-update-ceb8cac0bf  Step 2 - After 2FA is enabled, you then have to do the token swap.  Instructions for the token swap can be found here: https://medium.com/@vinchain/how-to-generate-keys-to-your-vinchain-wallet-6011bb616621  Reminder The security of your tokens is guaranteed by your private key, so as always please remember to keep your private key safe!  After the majority of the people will create a swap all the tokens will be distributed straight to the VINchain wallet! So do this as soon as possible in order to receive your tokens earlier!  Questions & Answers Q) What is a token swap? A) As you all know we will be using our own blockchain (not Etherium) and our own VINchain wallet that you can use to store your VIN tokens! In order for our tokens to be stored in your wallet, they first have to be converted from the Ethereum based tokens that they are now, into VINchain blockchain compatible tokens. This is known as a token swap.  Q) Why is a token swap necessary? A) You have to go through a token swap so that your tokens become tradable, transferable, and usable.  Q) Who has to do the token swap? A) Everyone has to go through a token swap  Update Also we have a small change in the amount of tokens burned. First of all some people have paid straight on our wallet so we will send 1,480,765.225 tokens to them. Second, some people have been paying from an exchange and 102,552.1135 tokens will be sent to them. Some people forgot to enter the ETH address and 77,730 tokens will be used for them. So in total we will have 840,108,901 tokens in total supply and 159,891,099 tokens will be burned.   Stay up to date Join our announcement group, https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements  all the news will be published here, so stay updated!

Body: More security for your account  As we continue to develop our platform, we continually add more useful features. Today we are happy to announce that we have added 2FA (two factor authentication) to all VINchain accounts (https://vinchain.io/account ). At this moment it is not mandatory to enable it (but it is very strongly recommended).  Very soon when our VINchain Wallet is live, it will be mandatory for everyone to protect their account with 2FA, so might as well enable it now Instructions can be found here: (https://medium.com/@vinchain/vinchain-logging-in-after-the-security-update-ceb8cac0bf ). It will takes just few minutes, so make sure your tokens and information stays safe!  Enable 2FA Security for your Account (https://vinchain.io/account )  If you have any questions join us on Telegram where you can get help any time a day (https://t.me/vinchainio). Body: The 24th Digital Dealer Expo - Results!  Hello VINchain community,  Our team and CEO were fortunate to visit the 24th Digital Dealer Expo, home to the cutting edge of the automotive industry, showcasing advancements in technology, latest trends and the most innovative companies. The conference was an incredible success as we were able to make many valuable connections, including business development professionals and the CIO of a large car auction company.     It’s been said opportunity looks a lot like hard work, and VINchain has been finding a lot of opportunity. During our ICO period, we’ve launched the alpha version of our system and mobile app, the VINchain wallet, and are in the process of completing our own blockchain. As our ICO period is coming to a close, we’ve collected over 10,000 Ethereum (ETH), and we couldn’t have met our goals without the support of our talented team and wonderful community.   If you have any questions join us on Telegram where you can get help any time a day (https://t.me/vinchainio). Join our community of over 13,000 people along with our CEO and founders to be part of the VINchain family.  Join our announcement group here: (https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements ). Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Congratulations everyone! VINchain was a successful ICO!  Dear VINchain community!  It has been a great pleasure to meet you and we thank you for your support. Our Initial Coin Offering (ICO) has ended after launching on February 1st. ICO was an amazing period for all of us as we met and surpassed all of our goals, including collecting the soft cap quickly enough that we are able to launch in the USA now. In total we have collected 12570 ETH thus far! Congratulations to all of you!  During ICO we have achieved a lot: our team grew significantly, we have more experts than ever who are helping us to build the system we envisioned! We have an incredible community, with a Telegram boasting over 7089 people. Thank you all dearly for your support.  We have been hard at work to make our vision a reality. We completed the alpha version of our system, along with the alpha version of the VINchain App. We launched our own blockchain and the VINchain wallet is available for use. We have everything needed to pursue the highest level of partnerships, and that’s exactly what we’re in the process of doing. We want to congratulate you all and say the biggest thanks for all your support.   After ICO, all news will be published on our announcement channel so follow us there to stay updated: (https://t.me/VINChainOfficialAnnouncements )  Join the conversation on social media:  Telegram - https://t.me/vinchainio Twitter - https://twitter.com/VINChain_io Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/vinchainio  Blogspot - https://vinchain.blogspot.com.by Medium - https://medium.com/@VINChain Bitcointalk - https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2349186.0 Github - https://github.com/VINChain

Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: $2,000,000 USD contribution to VINchain  Dear VINchain community,  Large projects like ours tend to have large investors backing them. One of our big backers from the very beginning has been A Better Bid - who invested $500,000 USD. Right now we are finalizing our agreement for them to increase their contribution to $2,000,000 USD!  A Better Bid (https://abetter.bid/en ) is an online car auction with more than 100,000+ vehicles on sale every day. It is a registered Copart Auto Auction broker which gives its clients access to the largest car auction inventory in USA, including used, repairable, theft recovery, fleet & lease, repo, flood and hail damaged cars.  Their contribution cannot be done all at once, and they will release the USD over the course of a year, so it will come steadily into our account. For the period of a year, the tokens that A Better Bid has reserved will be locked.  Our amazing partnership with A Better Bid is not only about financial support - we have a mutually beneficial relationship. They also provide us with access to their wealth of data that they have accumulated over many years of being in the vehicle auction business. We provide their clients with trusted vehicle history reports so they can feel confident in the car that they are about to purchase. Our partnerships always work both ways - we are always striving to make everything as beneficial for everyone as it is possible!  If you want to secure the most maximal discount that we offer, hurry and contribute to our project.  Contribute Now! (https://vinchain.io/account )  Detailed instructions on how to contribute can be found here: (https://vinchain.io/instructions)  We are really grateful for such amazing support from one of our biggest partners! With this we will be able to pursue new horizons and tackle new challenges in a way that would not be possible otherwise. We are all very excited to work with such amazing partners!  If you have any question don’t hesitate to contact us through telegram (https://t.me/vinchainio ). Help is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week—In fact, we are so serious about customer satisfaction, you can even talk to the CEO and founders firsthand. Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Bitcoin Garden: The influence of a blockchain on the level of safety and cost of a car https://bitcoingarden.org/the-influence-of-a-blockchain-on-the-level-of-safety-and-cost-of-a-car/  Since its inception, the blockchain technology has been incorporated into so many innovative ideas which are helping to solve key problems in the world. This subject has been discussed extensively on many social-economic and political platforms. The impact of having a decentralized operation can be widely seen through the various cryptocurrencies that are coming up. As more people gain knowledge about this technology and incorporate it into different ideas, it is clear that blockchain is more than just a system. At VinChain, the team is proud to be one of the leading startups that incorporate blockchain technology into increasing the safety of your car.  Nowadays blockchain technology allows to create a single database with all the information about the car. If you get your car repaired at an official repair shop, this information will be available to an insurance company that can give you a cheaper insurance plan. This is because the official repair shop guarantees the authenticity and reliability of installed spare parts. This is what company VinChain is working on. VinChain is creating a worldwide blockchain registry of used vehicle information that is 100% transparent, reliable, and accessible by everyone. The blockchain will guarantee that any information regarding a vehicle has not been falsified, changed, or deleted....

Now that we’ve set our sights on reaching the hard cap, we believe that Venture Hive is the next crucial ingredient in our recipe to success. They offer valuable connections and development opportunities to help spread the VINchain revolution globally. The community of entrepreneurs alone includes 31 startups in Miami from 18 different countries. They will help fast-track our goal of spreading to the United States and Europe as soon as possible. We will meet speakers with real-world experience who are experts at what they do and can help us get where we’re going.  We are excited to be in esteemed company — Venture Hive is supported by The World Bank, Microsoft, US Aid, the Knight Foundation, Cherry Bekaert, Fibernet Direct, US Small Business Administration, Miami-Dade County, the Miami World Center, Miami Downtown Development Authority, and the US State Department. Body: David Carp – Valuable Advisor for VINchain  VINchain wants to introduce you our new member of the team. David Carp is an automotive Veteran Executive. He had been working as a Director of Fleet, Remarketing & CPO for KIA Motors America, Inc for the last 15 years. David headed up both Fleet & Remarketing for Kia Motors; also he developed Kia’s CPO Program and led it for 11 years. It was the fastest growing CPO Program in the Industry.   He has over 25 years of experience. David’s automotive past includes working with Retail, Wholesale, Finance, Vehicle Valuation, Fleet & Remarketing. His automotive career started from selling Buick’s at Perry Buick in Norfolk, VA. He moved on to wholesale cars before joining the NADA-Official Used Car Guide Company as a responsible for the import of vehicle. David’s first work with a Manufacturer was Nissan/Infiniti Motor Corporation at a post of a Regional Remarketing Manager. He had a position in Remarketing with AutoNation USA and Vehicle Acquisition with CarMax. He was working with Saab Cars USA as their Remarketing Manager before joining the other Swedish carmaker Volvo Cars of North America as their Asset Remarketing Manager, the position he held before joining Kia. All this experience will help VINchain to achieve the final goals as soon as possible! Body: Dr. Simon Hassannia – VINchain Meets New Outstanding Adviser  Let me introduce you our new advisor - Dr. Simon Hassannia. Dr. Simon Hassannia has extensive management experience in consulting and industry in the areas automotive, telecommunications, consumer electronics and entertainment with focus on disruptive innovations and digital business. Currently as the Head of Business Innovation at ATU, the German’s leading automotive service provider with over $1 billion turnover, he is responsible for digital growth areas such as connected car, mobility-as-a-service and mobile solutions.  Previously he has worked as a Senior Business Consultant for Accenture Strategy and advised the management teams of major corporations regarding the digital transformation of the core business in communications, media and high-tech industries.  Priory he has worked as a digital expert for Deutsche Telekom (which includes brands such as T-Mobile) on the digital transformation of its European subsidiaries. In different positions he has developed innovation strategies, established agile methods and launched successfully digital services in the fields of IoT and Big Data. In various business projects he has consulted further companies such as Mercedes Benz, Universal Studios, LG Electronics, Bosch and Telefónica Germany with multinational assignments in Canada, China, Germany, Poland, Singapore, Spain and USA.  With a Ph.D. in digital innovation management at the University of Muenster (Germany) and executive programs at the University of California Berkeley and the INSEAD Business School, he is specialized in establishing digital platforms to empower the innovation performance of organizations. Furthermore, he is an author and a speaker on digital technologies such as Blockchain and VR/AR at conferences.  We are proud to have an honor to work with such a person and we are sure that this will bring new possibilities to our project! Body: VINchain Took Part in Miami Blockchain ICO Capital Summit  We’re eager to catch you up on a special event that VINchain took part in. We were fortunate to be invited to attend the Miami Blockchain ICO Capital Summit. It featured an executive charity golf event and was presented by Alternative Assets Events in association with Palm Beach Hedge Fund Association, Wall Street Research and CEO GOLF Club. It was a massive event that was held on the largest world stage for the high-level industry moguls and investors—In short, a great opportunity to educate like-minded individuals on what VINchain has to offer.  Our CEO and founder Alex Miles was selected to give a presentation detailing the future potential of blockchain technology and his unique vision on the topic. He spoke about the perspectives of the VINchain system and its necessity in the current and future landscape of the used vehicle market to a powerful reception.  This event was honored with the attendance of many valuable investors and enthusiasts who are interested in the incredible possibilities of blockchain technology. Alex made many valuable connections during this summit, which will surely grow into the partnerships as many of his past business relationships have. Networking opportunities like this are best way to spread word of the incredible potential of VINchain, and to attract people who are interested in the technology. Many already see the wealth of applications created by the VINchain’s decentralized database, and are ready to share their experience and excitement. We are grateful to have a platform to accelerate the development of VINchain, and spread knowledge of its potential throughout the world. Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: This is a good question. We are going to change the industry itself. Our reports will have many advantages. Author: DataAnalyst
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: I was thinking more about  what sources you're going to use to power your reports.  I'm looking at your alpha version report right now and I see that you have epic vin and ebay as a source, and data from both sorces is integrated in your report which is really messy as the data differs and it often repeats. On the other hand i found a few reports powered only with epicvin with no ebay data.  So for example, I'm looking at the VinChain Nissan Juke report and epicvin saying it's Juke trim S and ebay is sayin trim SV (correct). Also, Juke is a SUV and not the hatchback as your epicvin data claims...etc etc..  Furthermore, there is a vehicle history section in your report powered by ebay where you offer Carfax report !? - which is kinda funny.   I know this is alpha, but you guys need to find more trusted sources for these things if you want to be serious players - I'm a data expert in this field with almost 10 yrs of experience in the industry so I know what I'm talking about.

Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: We will be gathering information from all the possible sources: dealers and manufacturers, state entities (DMV), structural databases (like NMVTIS), insurance companies, vehicle history providers, vehicle owners, bank and leasing companies and our OBD device. We will try to have as many sources as possible so the report will include all the info about the car. And right now it’s just an alpha version; we will be working on organizing and structuring the data!

Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: VINchain ICO Opens to US Contributors   We are excited to announce that participation in the VINchain Initial Coin Offering (ICO) is officially open to United States based contributors.  Approximately one week ago the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) announced that it treats almost all Initial Coin Offerings (ICO’s) as securities. In a swift proactive response to this announcement, we had to temporarily limit the access of US residents in our ICO.  We had set our sights on overcoming this hurdle by the third quarter of 2018, so we are overjoyed to be able to announce that VINchain token purchasing is open to the US market as of February 14th, 2018. We were able to accomplish this major goal as VINchain was concluded to be a utility token and not a security.  VINchain tokens can be acquired here: https://vinchain.io/  VINchain tokens can be acquired with multiple currencies, including Ethereum (ETH), Bitcoin (BTC), Litecoin (LTC), and Dash (DASH).  The ICO opened on February 1st, and will continue until April 15th of 2018. Purchased VINchain tokens will be distributed between April 16th and April 23rd.     There’s never been a better time to get involved, with over 1,000,000 VINchain tokens sold already. The sooner you get involved, the greater bonus on top of your token purchase you will receive. We are currently in stage 2 of 7, which carries a corresponding bonus of 25% on top of your purchase (the current stage and bonus can be viewed anytime at vinchain.io). US contributors on the waitlist will receive the full bonus that was available at the time of signup!  One Ethereum (ETH) is equal to a base of 20,000 VINchain tokens, plus the bonus corresponding to the stage (+25% in stage 2), so currently one ETH purchases 25,000 VINchain tokens. Stages are progressed through when the specified amount of ETH is collected.  Please read our detailed, step by step instructions on how to get involved in the VINchain ICO here: https://vinchain.io/instructions  Many US-based contributors have been following our developments closely and are already excited to contribute, while others are hearing news of VINchain for the first time. VINchain offers a decentralized and secure vehicle history report built on the blockchain. This means that for the first time ever, consumers will be able to obtain reliable and transparent data on vehicles they are considering purchasing.  This reliability and transparency comes from the data being attached to a blockchain-passport specific to the VIN of the vehicle. Information about the vehicle is accumulated from databases of all system participants, including auto manufacturers (OEMs), insurance companies, service stations, banks, leasing companies, the vehicle itself and more. This information can be aggregated into a report which is purchased with VINchain tokens.  For more comprehensive and technical information, please consult the VINchain White Paper here: https://vinchain.io/files/VinChainWhitePaper.pdf  We’d love to chat and answer any questions or concerns you might have. For assistance, contact us on our Telegram at https://t.me/vinchainio.  Please join the conversation on social media!  Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/vinchainio/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/VINChain_io Blog: https://vinchain.blogspot.com/ Medium: https://medium.com/@VINChain

Body: Our New Adviser - Matt Carpenter the CFO at Audi of America and Audi Canada  Meet our new adviser - Matt Carpenter! He is the Chief Financial Officer at Audi of America and Audi Canada. He has extensive managerial experience in the automotive industry and years of working in this sphere. We are extremely happy that such a valuable person joined our team and we’re looking forward for new synergistic ideas that will be implemented in our project.  Matt’s professionalism speaks for itself, just by looking at his career path. From the very beginning he decided to connect his future with the automotive industry. Matt started his path with the Ford Motor Company in Michigan and worked there for 4.5 years as a Zone Manager.  In 2007 he began his journey with Audi of America as a Business Management Consultant at a Pied Piper Management Company LLC. His work there was stellar, so in 2007 he decided to shift gears and accepted the position of Vehicle Merchandising Manager at Audi of America. Not long after Matt joined Audi, he became responsible for control of finances in 2016. Then he became the Chief Financial Officer of Audi of America and Audi Canada.  Our project is growing bigger and we’re opening new offices and welcoming new members! And the fact that such an outstanding person decided to join us means a lot! With such a great team we will change the industry and create a new future for the automotive business!  Our ICO is live now! Author: Crashes
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Hello Lion1987 thank you for your question.  There are some fundamental differences between us. Yes both of us are doing vehicle history, but besides that almost nothing else is the same.  We see vehicle history as just a part of a much grander vision.   We are creating the future of connected cars, we just happened to start with vehicle history.  Today whenever you generate data, someone else profits from it. Think of facebook. They collect thousands of dollars worth of information from you, and you never see a cent.  Ultimately what we are doing is putting people in control of their own data.  We want to create a network of connected cars where all drivers worldwide are connected to VINchain. In this network all of the data that they generate belongs to them.  In this connected network, other business models can be built on top. Things like connecting to the drivers at the exact time when they need a specific service.  We are planning on generating revenue right after the launch of our solution  We have many great partners who are ready to do business with us. By the time of our launch their vehicle reports will be sourced by us. Also they will contribute their massive databases to us. So we are starting out ahead of the competition. Also they will accept our coins as a form of payment  We have much more experience than everyone else who is doing vehicle history on the blockchain, not just CarVertical. The combined auto experience of our core team members totals well over two decades! CarVerical cant say the same.  We have been around longer. If you check both of our BitcoinTalk branches, you will see that we were the first to come up with the idea.

Body: Meet Our New Valuable Advisor - Mark Taylor  We are extremely glad to say that we have made a partnership with such an experienced person as Mark Taylor, who is currently working as a head of business development department at PureCars. He is responsible for acquiring and managing strategic partnerships with the Automotive Manufacturers (OEMs). In addition, Mark identifies and manages strategic partnerships within the automotive marketing industry.  Prior to PureCars, Mark spent over 15 years with AutoNation, the largest Automotive Retailer in the US. During his tenure there, Mark headed up Business Development, where he worked to identify, negotiate, implement and manage AutoNation’s online strategic partnerships.  He carried out P&L responsibility for a budget of roughly $35M annually that drove top line revenues in excess of $3 Billion per annum. Was working closely with COO and SVP level executives to effectively communicate strategy, goals, and performance. He was also responsible for designing and implementation of various training and technology solutions that enhanced performance of the partnerships. During a significant period he was working closely with OEMs coordinating their digital strategies. Successfully managed a comprehensive, multi-million $ SEM program for roughly 300 locations.  Vinchain team is more than happy to have such a person as a partner in our project and we believe that Mark will help us to reach the highest success! Body: Vinchain Team is Going to Participate in UNLOCK  Al Iktissad Wal Aamal in partnership with Smart Dubai will be launching the UNLOCK Forum between January 14th-15th 2018 at Ritz Carlton Hotel DIFC. Because of the growing popularity of blockchain technology one of the richest city Dubai decided to start a year with such a forum.  UNLOCK will discuss how governments and private institutions in the MENA region can use blockchain applications to create a more efficient, competitive, smart government, smart economy and reinvent businesses. The implications of blockchain on the future of jobs and governments. The Forum will review the achievements of Dubai Government in implementing and piloting Blockchain solutions as well as their future plans.  We are going to present our project and to spread our idea among the people who are interested in such a technology. Our CEO Alex Miles will be there answering all your questions and explaining all the details. Body: Meet Our New Valuable Advisor  For any start-up, having a map of businesses which have done the same thing and succeeded is an honour. Ever since the beginning of our project, we have been privileged work with influential people in the world. We are happy to inform you that we have yet another addition to our team. Meet our new advisor Mr. Nissani who is a seasoned senior executive and has a proven track record of over 25 years across five continents in growing B2B and B2C companies. Mr. Nissani is a growth expert who serves as a board and advisory board member in several EU and Israeli high-tech and Blockchain companies (such as STOX.com), advising on strategy, marketing, operations and human capital management.  His abundant working experience includes being the Vice President managing 888.com’s high liquidity business unit which has revenues of close to $100M. He was also as an easy-forex Chief Marketing Officer where he managed sales and marketing budgets of tens of millions annually.  Mr Nissani also spent 5 years in venture capital and private equity with Poalim Capital Markets, the investment arm of Israel’s largest financial group – Poalim. He led investments in high-tech companies and assisted their management teams with both their strategy as well as their daily execution. In a nutshell, we are proud to have someone with such amazing talent and experience. As our advisor, Mr. Nissani will drive Vinchain to greater heights. Body: We became partners with the American company epicvin.com. This company has a big experience in providing vehicle history, and is also a member of the NIADA Auto Dealer Association. Also, epicvin.com cooperates with NMVTIS (National Motor Vehicle Title Information System). This organization collects and stores the history of vehicles in the US at the national level.  Here's the news about our new collaboration with epicvin.com: https://vinchain.io/blog/53 Also founders of this companies are in our team now. You can know more about our partnership using this link: https://vinchain.io/blog/55 Here you can read about the association NIADA: https://www.niada.com/ Here about NMVTIS: https://www.vehiclehistory.gov/

Author: VinChain
Title: 🚗🚕🚙🚌🚔🚍🚘🚖[ANN] VIN∞CHAIN🚔🚍🚘🚖VEHICLE HISTORY 🏎🚓🚑🚒🚐🚚🚛🚔🚍🚘🚖
Body: Car History Scams and How to Avoid Them  Cases of people being scammed for their car history are on the rise. The reality is that it can happen to anyone who decides to sell a car. Once you post an ad on the internet on any site, you become a target for them. If you are lucky, you will get an honest buyer. However, most of the times especially on sites such as Craigslist and Oodle, you are likely to get a scammer posing as an ‘interested buyer’. The interested buyer will find a way to make you pull up your car history from some website that they refer you to. The ultimate goal for the scammer is to get you to the site of which they get a commission from the lead. Once that’s done, they pretend to have changed their mind after you’ve bought your car history from their site.  And that’s not all. Many of the existing companies that provide data about used cars are also caught in the web of this violation of the law. Such a company is Carfax which is one of the biggest commercial suppliers of vehicle history reports to individuals and businesses on used cars. Carfax has always claimed to have information about the accidents for all the 50 states in the US. However, in 2006 it turned out that they were not able to check the information about accidents in 23 states. Even though the lawsuit was settled in May 2007 in the Trumbull County Common Pleas Court in Ohio, the fight against car history scams still continues. Carfax representative revealed that more than 10 million consumers were affected. The company asserts that it has major accident information from all 50 states and it backs up its claim with a buyback guarantee. The settlement in the West v. Carfax, Inc lawsuit was overturned and the lawyers for the class never pursued the case after that.  These are some of the problems Vinchain will solve through the decentralized vehicle database. With the help of this blockchain system, such situations are impossible to happen due to the decentralized system and absolute clarity of information.  Just to Remind Our token pre-sale started.
